(7387, 1063, 'texts', '<p>A gappy yellow smile is a thing of the past for this far North Queenslander</p>\r\n<p>Johnsâ€™ main concerns were his bleeding gums, discoloured teeth and the large very visible gap on the right side of his mouth.</p>\r\n'),
(7388, 1063, '_texts', 'field_26'),
(7389, 1065, 'texts', '<p>Young man with an ageing smile turns back the clock with modern dentistry</p>\r\n<p>A childhood bicycle accident left this charismatic man with broken teeth. Due to financial hardship and an ever expanding family, Chris McDermottâ€™s once dashing smile continued to deteriorate. Chrisâ€™ main concern was his broken patched up teeth.</p>\r\n'),
(7390, 1065, '_texts', 'field_26'),
(7391, 1067, 'texts', '<p>An unusual smile is restored to a natural youthful smile</p>\r\n<p>This young lady had uneven and unusual shaped teeth. Natashaâ€™s broken down metallic restorations were also causing her discomfort and a strange metallic taste.</p>\r\n'),
(7392, 1067, '_texts', 'field_26'),
(7393, 1068, 'texts', '<p>The Gold Coast girl known as ''toothy'' goes back to her glory days</p>\r\n<p>Traceyâ€™s main concern was her discoloured brown decayed teeth, in particular a white fleck on her front tooth. Often referred to as â€˜Toothyâ€™, Tracey wants to transform her smile to a younger more confident new look.</p>\r\n'),
(7394, 1068, '_texts', 'field_26'),
(7395, 1069, 'texts', '<p>Rugged country man longs for an even white smile</p>\r\n<p>Neilâ€™s main concerns were his yellow teeth and his uneven front teeth which he felt stuck out. Neil also suffered great discomfort and sensitivity from wearing out the sides of his teeth.</p>\r\n'),
(7396, 1069, '_texts', 'field_26'),
(7397, 1070, 'texts', '<p>Multi-coloured crooked smile disappears</p>\r\n<p>Johnâ€™s main concern was his multi-coloured crooked teeth with dark staining all around his mouth. He also had bleeding gums and missing teeth that were causing him great discomfort.</p>\r\n'),
(7398, 1070, '_texts', 'field_26'),
(7399, 1071, 'texts', '<p>Transformation into a swan with a spectacular new smile</p>\r\n<p>Robyn 44, came to Dr Yassmin highly embarrassed about her plate and discoloured upper teeth. She had individual teeth with varying colours due to the nature of several different treatments. Robyn desperately wanted to get rid of the partial plate which had caused her problems for over 10 years and she desired a whiter, more glamorous smile.</p>\r\n'),
(7400, 1071, '_texts', 'field_26'),
