(11, 1, '2015-08-13 05:19:54', '2015-08-13 05:19:54', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3><strong>DENTAL TREATMENTS HELP PATIENTS ACHIEVE A BEAUTIFUL, WHITE AND HEALTHY SMILE THAT LASTS FOR LIFE</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>How many times have you heard that impressions are very important?</h4>\r\n\r\nProbably far too many.\r\n\r\nThe thing is, your smile is key to making that first impression whether at job interviews or social gatherings.\r\n\r\nSo, why minimise your chances of making a great first impression when you could have a stellar smile to dazzle everyone?\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental, Dr Fadi Yassmin offers the latest innovations in dental treatments and modern cosmetic dentistry to achieve your celebrity smile.\r\n\r\nSometimes, a simple teeth whitening will make all the difference. Others, Dr Yassmin will need to combine a range of dental treatments to achieve the desired results, including\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dental Implants</li>\r\n<li>Dental Crowns</li>\r\n<li>Porcelain Dental Veneers</li>\r\n<li>Invisalign</li>\r\n<li>All On 4</li>\r\n<li>Implant retained dentures.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSome cases may require a comprehensive restorative treatment plan, incorporating more than one of the cosmetic dentistry treatments outlined above.\r\n\r\nThe expertise, experience and caring attitude of Dr. Fadi Yassmin is at the heart of our practice at Broadway Dental. You may know Dr. Yassmin from his many TV appearances, but there is much more to this renowned dentist than just television fame.\r\n\r\nFrom his earliest days in dental practice, Dr. Fadi Yassmin has been committed to honing his skills and continuing his education. He recently completed a Masterâ€™s in aesthetic dentistry program at the renowned King College in London, allowing him to stay at the top of the industry and better serve the needs of his patients.\r\n\r\nDr. Fadi Yassmin has also attended continuing education programs at prestigious educational institutions like the Australian Academy of Dento-Facial Aesthetics and UCLA.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Dental Treatments', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'treatments', '', '', '2015-09-29 00:00:12', '2015-09-29 00:00:12', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
