(125, 1, '2015-08-26 00:52:15', '2015-08-26 00:52:15', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>IMPROVING THE HEALTH AND BEAUTY OF YOUR SMILE</h3>\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental we are convinced that when you look great, you feel terrific.\r\n\r\nAnd of course, your smile is one of the features that can make the biggest impact on your appearance and on the way you interact with others - personally and professionally.\r\n\r\nBroadway Dental provides an extensive choice of cosmetic treatments, all of which can improve your oral health, and help create a beautiful Hollywood smile that you''ll be proud to show off wherever you go.\r\n\r\nWhether you''d simply like a brighter smile, or you could benefit from a complete smile makeover, the Broadway Dental Sydney team have the know-how and the technology to give you the smile design you''ve always dreamed of.\r\n\r\n<h3>What type of treatments do we use to achieve celebrity smiles?</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>DENTAL IMPLANTS</h4>\r\n\r\nAn excellent option for restoring one or more missing teeth, dental implants act as a solid new root for a new tooth restoration. Essentially tiny titanium screws, dental implants are surgically placed into your jawbone and secured once they have bonded. This creates a seamless look and feel and can greatly improve your smile and your overall looks.\r\n\r\nFollowing the dental implant procedure, Dr Yassmin can then restore your tooth using a porcelain crown or bridge. After the crown or bridge is in place, you can once again enjoy a complete, healthy and natural-looking smile.\r\n\r\n<h4>INVISALIGN</h4>\r\n\r\nIf you''d like a straighter, more even smile but you''ve been put off by the clumsy look of traditional braces, Invisalign is the answer.\r\n\r\nInvisalign uses clear, medical-grade plastic aligners that are practically invisible, to gradually and efficiently straighten your teeth without any heavy metal brackets. It''s also completely removable, so that you can take your aligners out to eat, brush and floss as normal.\r\n\r\nNow you can join the hundreds of adult patients we''ve helped achieve a more beautiful, straighter smile - invisibly.\r\nIf you would like to find out how Invisalign could give you the smile you''ve always wanted, just give us a call and speak to the Broadway Dental team to arrange your personal consultation today.\r\n\r\n<h4>DENTAL BONDING</h4>\r\n\r\nOne of our most cost-effective cosmetic dental procedures, dental bonding uses tooth-coloured resin to repair or improve the appearance of your teeth.Dental bonding may be a smart option:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Restore decayed, chipped or cracked teeth</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	<li>Lighten discoloured teeth</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Change the shape of teeth</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Protect your tooth''s root if your gums have receded</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Provide alternatives to traditional porcelain veneers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\nDr Yassmin will select the coloured composite resin that most closely matches your natural tooth. The resin will then be applied and hardened with a special light to securely bond the material to your tooth. Once the material has hardened, Dr Yassmin will shape and trim the resin, and finally polish it to a sheen which, closely matches the rest of your natural tooth.\r\n\r\nBroadway Dental Sydney offers dental bonding to improve the look of your smile without the need for expensive and expensive custom-made tooth restorations. The procedure is completely straightforward, and most patients require no anaesthesia to remain comfortable throughout the procedure.\r\n\r\n<h4>TEETH WHITENING</h4>\r\n\r\nMany simple everyday actions like drinking tea, coffee and red wine, or smoking, can stain your teeth and leave you with a dull smile you''ll be hesitant to show off.\r\n\r\nThe Broadway Dental Teeth Whitening treatment will lighten your teeth by up to 12 shades, improving your self-confidence and giving you a dazzling new smile you''ll be proud to share with the world.\r\n\r\nWe offer two very safe and effective methods of teeth whitening:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>  In-chair whitening - you will be able to enjoy a new smile in just over an hour</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>At-home treatments - improve the colour of your smile in as little as two weeks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>DENTAL VENEERS</h4>\r\n\r\nStained, discoloured and crooked teeth can wreck your confidence and lower your self-esteem, but you do not have to live with the shame one day longer. At Broadway Dental, we can provide the dental veneers you need to restore your bright white smile, your appearance and your self-confidence.\r\n\r\nOur dental veneers, including traditional, porcelain and composite options, can also restore your great smile if your teeth are chipped, broken or worn. Even if your teeth are gappy or misaligned, our porcelain dental veneers can restore your great smile and give you the confidence you need to face the world.\r\n\r\nOur custom-made dental veneers are durable yet incredibly thin. Once these thin porcelain shells are bonded to your teeth securely, it will give them a natural look and feel. You will not even know you are wearing them - and neither will anyone else.\r\n\r\nIt will not take much time to transform your smile from embarrassing to bright and white. Even if your teeth or chipped, cracked or damaged, our custom-made dental veneers can transform your smile in just two appointments.\r\n\r\n<h4>SLEEP DENTISTRY</h4>\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental, we offer a full range of sleep and sedation dentistry, including traditional sleep dentistry, the latest in sedation dentistry and GA. These practices are perfect for the fearful dental patient, but they can be a wonderful choice even for men and women who are comfortable with regular dental care.\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental, we understand that a simple trip to the dentist is not so simple for many patients. Whether it is a bad experience in the past or just a generalized fear of the dentist chair, we understand the trepidation many patients experience when scheduling dental care.\r\n\r\nThat is why we work so hard to ease the fears of our patients - and why we offer a full range of options designed to eliminate pain and reduce the fear associated with dental care. From sleep dentistry to sedation and GA, Broadway Dental offers a full range of services designed to help you sit back, relax and regain your healthy smile.\r\n\r\nPatients who have tried sleep dentistry typically wonder what all the fuss was about. Far from being fearful, these patients actually look forward to their dental appointments. They know they will experience no pain - and they know that in the end they will emerge with a bright white smile they will be proud to show their friends, family members and co-workers.\r\n\r\nSome patients worry about the loss of control they will feel when undergoing cosmetic or therapeutic procedures using sleep dentistry, but they need not fret. When undergoing sleep dentistry treatment, the patient has the sensation of being asleep, but they remain awake and able to respond to the dentist at all times. This makes the dental procedures more effective and safer for everyone involved.\r\n\r\n<b>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</b>\r\n[su_accordion]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="What is cosmetic dentistry?" style="fancy"] Simply put, cosmetic dentistry refers to the art and science used at Broadway Dental to create a more beautiful smile for you.\r\n\r\nCosmetic dentistry can lighten stained teeth, correct crooked or replace missing teeth, or create a complete smile makeover.\r\n\r\nSmile design from Broadway Dental Sydney starts with a personalised cosmetic dentistry treatment plan, based on the needs and goals you have for your smile. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="How can cosmetic dentistry improve my smile??" style="fancy"]If youâ€™re living with teeth which are damaged, worn or need rebuilding, we may recommend Dental Crowns, Inlays or Onlays.\r\n\r\nTo improve the colour or shape of your teeth, dental veneers, Teeth Whitening or bonding could be the right option for you.\r\n\r\nIf you are missing teeth, we can use Dental Implants, Bridges or Dentures to restore your smile.\r\n\r\nWe will evaluate your personal situation and help you decide on the right combination of treatments for your smile. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="Why are my teeth becoming darker as I get older?" style="fancy"] \r\n      \r\n      Many factors act upon your teeth to make them look dull and less bright over time:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Plaque tends to build up faster and more heavily as we age</li>\r\n<li> Red wine, tea and coffee will stain your teeth the more you drink them</li>\r\n<li>The dentin that makes up your teeth will also change and darken naturally over time</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAll of these factors can be addressed with the help of professional teeth whitening from Broadway Dental.\r\n      \r\n      \r\n       [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="How long will my teeth whitening treatment last?" style="fancy"]As with any dental procedure, your results will depend on your individual situation, and your oral care routine post-treatment. Continuing with the habits that stained your teeth in the first place, such as drinking coffee or red wine, or especially smoking, will gradually stain your teeth again over time. Avoiding these habits, and visiting Broadway Dental for periodic touch-up treatment, can help preserve your white new smile. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="Is cosmetic dentistry right for me?" style="fancy"]Thanks to the extensive range of advanced dental procedures and technology available today, almost anyone can benefit from cosmetic dentistry in our Sydney practice.\r\n\r\nSo whether youâ€™d like a brighter smile, or whether you need to replace missing teeth, your first step is to arrange a consultation with Dr Yassmin and the Broadway Dental team. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[/su_accordion]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Cosmetic Dentistry', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cosmetic-dentistry', '', '', '2015-09-29 00:04:21', '2015-09-29 00:04:21', '', 11, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=125', 0, 'page', '', 0),
