(127, 1, '2015-08-26 00:52:24', '2015-08-26 00:52:24', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h4>REATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ TEETH WHITENING</h4>\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you get the feeling that your teeth are obstructing success in your personal and professional lives?</strong>\r\n\r\nWhile regular dental care at home can help prevent some oral diseases, the effect of a number of external agents like red wine, tea or coffee â€“ or the more serious habit of smoking â€“ can stain your teeth and dull your smile over the years.\r\n\r\nSydneyâ€™s leading cosmetic dentist, Dr Fadi Yassmin, will draw a brand new smile for you with his range of teeth whitening treatments. In fact, you probably wonâ€™t believe how quickly youâ€™ll be able to enjoy a naturally white smile, and the tremendous self-confidence boost that comes with it!\r\n\r\nAs simple as relaxing in one of Broadway Dentalâ€™s elegant treatment lounges while watching TV or listening to music and letting the whitening gel do its magic for about 20 minutes.\r\n\r\nIn-chair or At-home Teeth whitening â€“ start making an impression wherever you go!\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Teeth Whitening', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'whitening', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:36:45', '2015-09-11 10:36:45', '', 16, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=127', 0, 'page', '', 0),
