(214, 1, '2015-08-26 02:08:54', '2015-08-26 02:08:54', '<h2>The Treatment You Need<br>Without The Pain</h2>\r\n<div class="text">\r\n\r\n									<p><iframe width="390" height="219" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/fNEXBiPsF5E?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;controls=1&amp;autohide=1"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>For some people the overwhelming fear of dental appointments can cause anxiety and lead to postponing much needed treatment. This may stem from previous bad experiences, a misunderstanding of dental procedures or a lack of knowledge of modern treatments and options.</p>\r\n<p>The comfort, relaxation and happiness of our patients is foremost for Dr Yassmin, and the entire Broadway Dental team will do whatever they can to reduce your anxiety, alleviate any fears and provide painless, quick treatments.</p>\r\n<p><strong>One such option is Sleep Dentistry.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Often referred to as pain free dentistry, twilight sedation, dental sedation or sedation dentistry, this innovative form of sedation dentistry is a safe and highly effective technique used to overcome the fear, anxiety and discomfort that so often accompanies a visit to the dentist.</p>\r\n<p>Sleep Dentistry combines sedative and pain relieving medication which, is intravenously administered and supervised by an experienced medical doctor and has patients virtually asleep throughout the entire procedure.</p>\r\n<p><strong>When should Sleep Dentistry be applied?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Sleep Dentistry is recommended for patients who:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Dislike needles,</li>\r\n<li>Have a low pain threshold,</li>\r\n<li>Have difficulty getting numb,</li>\r\n<li>Dislike noises, smells and tastes associated with dental treatments,</li>\r\n<li>Have gag reflexes,</li>\r\n<li>Present jaw problems,</li>\r\n<li>Require long treatment sessions,</li>\r\n<li>Are undergoing a lengthy procedure or wish to complete several procedures in a single appointment visit.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sleep Dentistry can take the anxiety out of your dental procedure or help you complete several procedures at once so you get the treatment you need and the beautiful healthy smile you have always wanted.</p>\r\n<p>Ask us how you can sleep through your next dental visit and wake up with a gorgeous smile.</p>\r\n\r\n									\r\n										<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://www.broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n\r\n									\r\n									', 'Sleep Dentistry', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sleep-dentistry', '', '', '2015-09-04 05:43:21', '2015-09-04 05:43:21', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=214', 0, 'page', '', 0),
