(232, 1, '2015-08-26 02:23:21', '2015-08-26 02:23:21', '\r\n									<p><strong>How much does Invisalign cost?</strong></p>\r\n<p>The cost of an Invisalign treatment depends on individual circumstances but for most of our patients at Broadway Dental, the cost of a full treatment ranges between $5,000 and $10,000. </p>\r\n<p>After our initial consultation weâ€™ll be able to provide you with a treatment plan detailing all costs for your specific needs.</p>\r\n<p>If your health insurance policy has orthodontic coverage, Invisalign should be covered to a similar extent as conventional braces.</p>\r\n<p><strong>To book your free consultation with Dr Fadi Yassmin today, call <span class="AVANSERnumber">(02) 9281 0100</span> or via</strong> <a href="mailto:info@broadwaydental.com.au">email</a>. </p>\r\n<p><strong>See our Invisalign success stories</strong></p>\r\n\r\n									\r\n										<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://www.broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n\r\n									\r\n								\r\n									\r\n									\r\n									\r\n										\r\n\r\n										<a class="book-now" href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/gallery/invisalign/">See Our Invisalign Success Stories</a>\r\n\r\n	', 'Invisalign Cost', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'invisalign-cost', '', '', '2015-09-07 01:22:56', '2015-09-07 01:22:56', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=232', 0, 'page', '', 0),
