ctitioners in the city.\r\nCommitted to deliver the latest treatments in cosmetic dentistry and general oral healthcare in a warm, relaxing environment, Dr Yassmin has remained at the forefront in all areas of dentistry, including:\r\n<ul class="arrow-inline">\r\n	<li>Cosmetic Dentistry</li>\r\n	<li>Smile Makeovers</li>\r\n	<li>InvisalignÂ®</li>\r\n	<li>Dental Implants</li>\r\n	<li>Teeth Whitening</li>\r\n	<li>Sleep Dentistry</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>His philosophy</strong>\r\n\r\nPassionate about transforming peopleâ€™s lives through general and cosmetic dentistry, Dr Yassminâ€™s philosophy centres around the importance of listening to his patients concerns, needs and goals and informing them clearly and with all honestly about the best choices available to them.\r\n\r\nAs such, Dr Yassmin spends all the time that is needed for him to build a solid, long-term relationship with his patients. At Broadway Dental there is no rushing or half-done jobs.\r\n\r\nSimilarly, Dr Yassmin understands that to be able to customise the best dental treatment for each of his patients, he needs to stay at the forefront of modern dentistry. Thatâ€™s why, Broadway Dental invests significantly in cutting-edge dental technology and advanced training for all members of the team.\r\n\r\n<strong>His training</strong>\r\n\r\nSince graduating from Sydney University in 1993, Dr Yassmin has always felt passionate about excelling in his career. After founding Broadway Dental in 1998, he knew he had to stay informed about national and international developments in his field, and remain constantly up-to-date with the latest technological advancements to best serve his patients.\r\n\r\nThatâ€™s why Dr Yassmin constantly invests in ongoing education and post graduate courses both in Australia and overseas, including his recent completion of a Masters in Dento-facial Aesthetics. This revolutionary new facet of cosmetic dentistry goes beyond creating a traditional smile makeover. Using the most up-to-