pain-free dentistry</h4>\r\nUsing the latest technology and advances in cosmetic dentistry procedures that are absolutely pain-free and non-invasive, Dr Yassmin is able to deliver restorative and cosmetic dentistry to correct, restore, enhance and maintain his patientsâ€™ smile.\r\n\r\nSleep dentistry administered by a highly qualified Sydney anaesthetist who works alongside Dr Yassmin, is also available for patients who are particularly apprehensive about dental procedures or who will be undergoing long-term procedures.\r\n<h4>An outstanding team of dental care practitioners</h4>\r\nCommitted to undergo continuous professional development in order to provide the highest standards of dentistry, Dr Fadi Yassmin regularly attends advanced training at a number of leading dental institutes, including the renowned Kings College, the Australian Academy of Dento-Facial Aesthetics and, UCLA â€“ one of the worldâ€™s leading medical centres.\r\n\r\nThe exceptional team at Broadway Dental will make you feel like a star before, during and after your visit.\r\n\r\n<strong>Book your free consultation</strong> with Dr Fadi Yassmin today by calling <strong>(02) 9281 0100</strong> or<strong><a href="mailto:info@broadwaydental.com.au"> via email</a></strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-01 01:37:45', '2015-09-01 01:37:45', '', 9, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
