(481, 1, '2015-09-02 03:23:18', '2015-09-02 03:23:18', '<h2>Sydney Dental specialist Dr Fadi Yassmin comments on recent increased interest in INVISALIGN technology</h2>\r\n<h1>HARPERS BAZAAR BRIDES</h1>\r\nZara Phillips let her rugby-star groom, Mike Tindall, wear invisible braces down the aisle, so weâ€™ll take that as a royal seal of approval. Invisalign (www.invisalign.com.au) will straighten your smile and if youâ€™re still wearing them on the day, they wonâ€™t show up in photos like traditional braces. â€œWeâ€™ve noticed a huge increase in demand [from] brides-to-be,â€ says Dr Fadi Yassmin at Broadway Dental in Sydney.', 'Harpers Bazaar Brides', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'harpers-bazaar-brides', '', '', '2015-09-02 08:40:13', '2015-09-02 08:40:13', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?post_type=article&#038;p=481', 0, 'article', '', 0),
