(632, 1, '2015-09-04 00:47:49', '2015-09-04 00:47:49', '<div class="crown-text">\r\n			\r\n			<div>\r\n				<p>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME - DENTAL CROWNS</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Living with the stigma of a broken tooth?</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>You don''t have to.</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Not with the very natural-looking Dental Crowns available from Broadway Dental.</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Dental Crowns (or caps) are designed to cover or ''cap'' a tooth to restore it to its normal shape and size, strengthening and improving its appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Visit us at Broadway Dental to find out about Dental Crowns and you too, could be on your way to sharing an A-list smile with the rest of the world!</p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n </div>', 'Crowns', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '168-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 00:47:49', '2015-09-04 00:47:49', '', 168, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/168-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(633, 1, '2015-09-11 10:11:33', '2015-09-11 10:11:33', '<h4>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ DENTAL VENEERS</h4>\n\n<p>Do you get the feeling people judge you on your smile?</p>\n\n<p>A gorgeous smile will open new doors for you, improve your confidence, your personal relationships, and your ability to communicate.</p>\n\n<p>Now you can achieve the smile you always wanted with Porcelain Veneers.</p>\n\n<p>What are Porcelain Veneers?</p>\n\n<p>Constructed from strong, high quality porcelains that closely mimic the many shades and translucencies found in natural teeth, each Dental Veneer consists of a thin porcelain shell which fits perfectly well over the front surfaces of your teeth. Once in position, veneers can help create a flawless smile, specifically designed to match your preferred look.</p>\n\n<p>Whether to hide minor chips or cracks to teeth, misaligned teeth, gaps, irregularly shaped teeth or whether to give a fresh new look to your discoloured or stained teeth, Dental Veneers are an excellent way to help improve your smile.</p>\n', 'Dental Venners', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:11:33', '2015-09-11 10:11:33', '', 264, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/264-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
