(635, 1, '2015-09-04 01:08:47', '2015-09-04 01:08:47', 'CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ WHITE FILLINGS\r\n\r\nEmbarrassed about your obvious tooth decay?\r\n\r\nDonâ€™t let it stop you from having a perfectly normal and satisfactory personal and professional lives.\r\nWhite Fillings are a great treatment for the restoration of decayed teeth.\r\n\r\nHaving become the preferred option for the treatment of cavities today, White Fillings are a much improved alternative to earlier large long-term mercury fillings, providing a more natural tooth-like appearance.\r\n\r\nVisit us at Broadway Dental to find out about white fillings and you too, could be on your way to sharing an A-list smile with the rest of the world!\r\n', 'White Fillings', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '166-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 01:08:47', '2015-09-04 01:08:47', '', 166, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/166-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(636, 1, '2015-09-04 01:11:56', '2015-09-04 01:11:56', 'CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ DENTAL IMPLANTS\r\n\r\nFacing the world with missing teeth may have severe negative psychological consequences that extend much beyond the mere difficulties eating or speaking. Missing teeth may lead to a very damaging lack of self-confidence in social and professional situations.\r\n\r\nDental Implants can help you regain the ability to interact socially with confidence.\r\n\r\nAn extremely strong artificial tooth root that is submerged into the jawbone, dental implants are a much more comfortable and natural option than traditional dentures and aesthetically, they do resemble a normal tooth root.\r\n\r\nSo, whether you need to restore one or more missing teeth, anchor a dental bridge or support a full denture, dental implants might be the right option for you.\r\n\r\nLet Dr Yassmin and his team at Broadway Dental assess whether dental implants are the perfect treatment to give you a smile which is whole, healthy, and attractive once again.\r\n', 'Dental Implants', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '129-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 01:11:56', '2015-09-04 01:11:56', '', 129, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/129-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(637, 1, '2015-09-04 01:34:43', '2015-09-04 01:34:43', 'REATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ TEETH WHITENING\r\n\r\nDo you get the feeling that your teeth are obstructing success in your personal and professional lives?\r\n\r\nWhile regular dental care at home can help prevent some oral diseases, the effect of a number of external agents like red wine, tea or coffee â€“ or the more serious habit of smoking â€“ can stain your teeth and dull your smile over the years.\r\n\r\nSydneyâ€™s leading cosmetic dentist, Dr Fadi Yassmin, will draw a brand new smile for you with his range of teeth whitening treatments. In fact, you probably wonâ€™t believe how quickly youâ€™ll be able to enjoy a naturally white smile, and the tremendous self-confidence boost that comes with it!\r\n\r\nAs simple as relaxing in one of Broadway Dentalâ€™s elegant treatment lounges while watching TV or listening to music and letting the whitening gel do its magic for about 20 minutes.\r\n\r\nIn-chair or At-home Teeth whitening â€“ start making an impression wherever you go!\r\n', 'Teeth Whitening', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 01:34:43', '2015-09-04 01:34:43', '', 127, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/127-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
