(648, 1, '2015-09-04 01:46:10', '2015-09-04 01:46:10', 'CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ TOOTH BONDING\r\n\r\nEmbarrassed by chipped or cracked teeth? Uncomfortable about the appearance of your discoloured smile?\r\nTooth bonding can give your tired smile a new breath of life applying.\r\n\r\nTypically used for cosmetic purposes to improve the appearance of a discoloured or chipped tooth, tooth bonding consists in applying a tooth-coloured resin material to the tooth using adhesives and a high intensity curing light. The procedure gets its name because materials are bonded to the tooth. Bonding is typically used for.\r\n\r\nSo, whether you need to close spaces between teeth, repair decayed, chipped or cracked teeth or whether you need to improve the appearance of discoloured teeth, book your consultation with Dr Fadi Yassmin today.\r\n', 'Bonding', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '174-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 01:46:10', '2015-09-04 01:46:10', '', 174, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/174-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
