able, so that you can take your aligners out to eat, brush and floss as normal.</p>\r\n<p>Now you can join the hundreds of adult patients weâ€™ve helped achieve a more beautiful, straighter smile &ndash; invisibly.<br>\r\n#To find out how Invisalign could give you the smile youâ€™ve always wanted, speak to the Broadway Dental team to arrange your personal consultation today.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Call (02) 9281 0100 or <a href="mailto:info@broadwaydental.com.au">email</a> Broadway Dental now.</strong></p>\r\n<h2>DENTAL BONDING</h2>\r\n<p>One of our most cost-effective cosmetic dental procedures, dental bonding uses tooth-coloured resin to repair or improve the appearance of your teeth.</p>\r\n<p>Dental bonding may be a smart option:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To restore decayed, chipped or cracked teeth,</li>\r\n<li>Lighten discoloured teeth,</li>\r\n<li>Change the shape of teeth or,</li>\r\n<li>To protect your toothâ€™s root if your gums have receded.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Dr Yassmin will select a coloured composite resin that closely matches your tooth. The resin will then be applied and hardened with a special light to securely bond the material to your tooth. Once the material has hardened, Dr Yassmin will shape and trim the resin, and finally polish it to a sheen which, closely matches the rest of your natural tooth.</p>\r\n<p>In just 30 to 60 minutes at Broadway Dental Sydney, dental bonding will improve the look of your smile without any need for expensive, custom made tooth restorations. The procedure is completely straightforward, and usually you wonâ€™t need any anaesthetic to remain entirely comfortable.</p>\r\n<p>Keen to find out more about Dental Bonding?</p>\r\n<p>Call the Broadway Dental team on <strong><span class="AVANSERnumber">(02) 9281 0100</span></strong></p>\r\n<h2>TEETH WHITENING</h2>\r\n<p>Many simple everyday actions like drinking tea, coffee and red wine, or smoking, can stain your teeth and leave you with a dull smile youâ€™ll be hesitant to show off.</p>\r\n<p>The Broadway Dental Teeth Whitening treatment will lighten your teeth by up to 12 shades, improving your self-confidence and giving you a dazzling new smile youâ€™ll be proud to share with the world.</p>\r\n<p>We offer two very safe and effective methods of teeth whitening:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>In-chair whitening &ndash; you will be able to enjoy a new smile in just over an hour,</li>\r\n<li>At-home treatments &ndash; improve the colour of your smile in as little as two weeks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Naturally, the Broadway Dental Sydney team will be happy to give you the advice you need to select the best method for whitening your smile.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Book your consultation with Dr Fadi Yassmin today</strong> <a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">here</a> <strong>and discover whether you are eligible for our Teeth Whitening treatments.</strong></p>\r\n<h2>DENTAL VENEERS</h2>\r\n<p>If you have teeth that are discoloured, worn, chipped or broken, or a smile that is uneven, gappy or misaligned, Porcelain Dental veneers can be a stunning restorative solution.</p>\r\n<p>These custom-made, incredibly thin porcelain shells are securely bonded onto the front of your teeth to create an even, natural looking, and very attractive smile.</p>\r\n<p>Best of all, you can enjoy all the benefits of dental veneers in just two appointments with Broadway Dental Sydney. Find out how by calling the Broadway Dental team on <strong>(02) 9281 0100</strong> today.</p>\r\n<h2>SLEEP DENTISTRY</h2>\r\n<p>For some of our patients, a simple visit to the friendly Broadway Dental team can be a nerve-wracking experience.<br>\r\nIf this is the case for you too, we understand that the thought of undergoing a complex cosmetic dentistry treatment may be unbearable. Thatâ€™s why we are pleased to offer you Sleep Dentistry, currently the most advanced form of dental sedation.</p>\r\n<p>With Sleep Dentistry you will have the sensation of being asleep during your treatment, when in fact, you will be awake and able to respond to your dentistâ€™s requests at all times.</p>\r\n<p>After trying Sleep Dentistry you may even wonder what all the fuss about dental treatments was about!<br>\r\nYou can ask us about your sedation options, including sleep dentistry, here.</p>\r\n<h2>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h2>\r\n<p><strong>What is cosmetic dentistry?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simply put, cosmetic dentistry refers to the art and science used at Broadway Dental to create a more beautiful smile for you.</p>\r\n<p>Cosmetic dentistry can lighten stained teeth, correct crooked or replace missing teeth, or create a complete smile makeover.</p>\r\n<p>Smile design from Broadway Dental Sydney starts with a personalised cosmetic dentistry treatment plan, based on the needs and goals you have for your smile.</p>\r\n<p><strong>How can cosmetic dentistry improve my smile?</strong></p>\r\n<p>If youâ€™re living with teeth which are damaged, worn or need rebuilding, we may recommend Dental Crowns, Inlays or Onlays.</p>\r\n<p>To improve the colour or shape of your teeth, dental veneers, Teeth Whitening or bonding could be the right option for you.</p>\r\n<p>If you are missing teeth, we can use Dental Implants, Bridges or Dentures to restore your smile.</p>\r\n<p>We will evaluate your personal situation and help you decide on the right combination of treatments for your smile.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why are my teeth becoming darker as I get older?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Many factors act upon your teeth to make them look dull and less bright over time:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Plaque tends to build up faster and more heavily as we age.</li>\r\n<li>Red wine, tea and coffee will stain your teeth the more you drink them.</li>\r\n<li>The dentin that makes up your teeth will also change and darken naturally over time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>All of these factors can be addressed with the help of professional Teeth Whitening from Broadway Dental.</p>\r\n<p><strong>How long will my Teeth Whitening treatment last?</strong></p>\r\n<p>As with any dental procedure, your results will depend on your individual situation, and your oral care routine post-treatment. Continuing with the habits that stained your teeth in the first place, such as drinking coffee or red wine, or especially smoking, will gradually stain your teeth again over time. Avoiding these habits, and visiting Broadway Dental for periodic touch-up treatment, can help preserve your white new smile.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Is cosmetic dentistry right for me?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Thanks to the extensive range of advanced dental procedures and technology available today, almost anyone can benefit from cosmetic dentistry in our Sydney practice.</p>\r\n<p>So whether youâ€™d like a brighter smile, or whether you need to replace missing teeth, your first step is to arrange a consultation with Dr Yassmin and the Broadway Dental team. After that, itâ€™ll be smooth sailing towards a brand new You.</p>\r\n\r\n									\r\n										<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://www.broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n\r\n									\r\n									\r\n									\r\n									\r\n									', 'Cosmetic Dentistry', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 05:18:22', '2015-09-04 05:18:22', '', 125, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/125-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(690, 1, '2015-09-04 05:29:18', '2015-09-04 05:29:18', '\r\n\r\n									<div itemprop="video" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/VideoObject">\r\n<h2><span itemprop="name">All on Four Dental Implants</span> Explained:</h2>\r\n<p>     <meta itemprop="duration" content="T04M39S"><meta itemprop="thumbnailUrl" content="http://i.ytimg.com/vi/8pn3eV8euwU/hqdefault.jpg"><meta itemprop="contentURL" content="https://www.youtube.com/v/8pn3eV8euwU"><meta itemprop="embedURL" content="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8pn3eV8euwU"><br>\r\n     <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8pn3eV8euwU?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;controls=1&amp;autohide=1" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="197" width="351"></iframe><br>\r\n     </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Living with the stigma that comes with missing teeth? Too embarrassed to be seen in public without your full smile?</p>\r\n<p>For many years dentures have been the preferred solution for the replacement of missing teeth:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Complete dentures are used by people who have lost all their natural upper or lower teeth.</li>\r\n<li>Partial dentures are for patients who still retain some of their natural teeth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Although dentures are still popular, Dental Implants are quickly becoming one of the most sought after tooth replacement options today. Replicating a missing tooth root, Dental Implants are fine titanium screws or rods that are placed into the jawbone.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The latest innovation in modern dentistry- All-on-4</strong></p>\r\n<p>Bringing dentures and dental implants together, All-On-4 Implant Retained Dentures, enable patients to have a set of upper or lower dentures permanently secured, sometimes with as few as four Dental Implants.</p>\r\n<p><strong>How is this achieved?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Simply by placing two of the four implants at an angle at the front of the mouth where the jawbone is denser and stronger.</p>\r\n<p><strong>How do I maintain my All-on-4 Implant Retained Dentures?</strong></p>\r\n<p>After receiving your All-on-4 Implant Retained Dentures, it is essential you follow a thorough at-home brushing and flossing routine. You should also schedule regular appointment check-ups every six months with Dr Yassmin to ensure your implants remain strong.</p>\r\n<p>To learn more about <strong>All-on-4</strong> and find out if youâ€™re an ideal candidate to use them, schedule a consultation appointment with Dr Yassmin who will explain the procedure in non-medical terms and gladly answer any of your questions.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Please note:</strong> Any surgical or invasive procedure carries risks. Before proceeding, you should seek a second opinion from an appropriately qualified health practitioner.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n									\r\n								', 'ALL-ON-4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '131-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-04 05:29:18', '2015-09-04 05:29:18', '', 131, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/131-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
