(749, 1, '2015-09-10 03:45:24', '2015-09-10 03:45:24', '<div class="inner-content">\r\n							<div class="logo-2"><a title="Dentist Sydney" href="http://broadwaydental.com.au"></a></div>\r\n							<div class="seen"><img alt="" src="http://broadwaydental.com.au/wp-content/themes/broadway/images/seen.png"></div>\r\n							<div class="content">\r\n								<div class="text">Dr Yassmin and the Broadway Dental team were featured on the popular TV programme â€˜10 Years Younger in 10 Daysâ€™. They were one of the expert teams that helped transform the lives of people by giving them dazzling new smile makeovers using a variety of dental procedures.</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n							<h1>10 Years Younger In 10 Days</h1>\r\n							<div class="pagination">MORE EPISODES <span class="page-numbers current">1</span>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/2/" class="page-numbers">2</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/3/" class="page-numbers">3</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/4/" class="page-numbers">4</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/5/" class="page-numbers">5</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/6/" class="page-numbers">6</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/7/" class="page-numbers">7</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/8/" class="page-numbers">8</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/9/" class="page-numbers">9</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/10/" class="page-numbers">10</a>\r\n<a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/category/10-years-younger-in-10-days/page/11/" class="page-numbers">11</a></div>\r\n							<div class="post-main">\r\n			