(753, 1, '2015-09-10 06:02:49', '2015-09-10 06:02:49', '<div class="treatments">\r\n								<h2>Treatment provided</h2>\r\n								<div class="treatments-provided">\r\n									<ul>\r\n<li>Photos and Radiographic records</li>\r\n<li>Photos and radiographic records were taken to allow accurate assessment of the existing dentition (development and arrangement of teeth in his mouth) and to give Wayne a visual view of the treatment needed.</li>\r\n<li>Preventative care (Dental prophylaxis)</li>\r\n<li>Deep scaling and polishing to remove the buildup of heavy plaque (also known as calculus and tartar) and staining on Wayne''s teeth, helping prevent cavities and gum disease</li>\r\n<li>Oral hygiene routine - Cariscreen and caries free rinse program. Custom trays of GC tooth mousse were created for home use, which will help prevent tooth decay (that can lead to cavities, pain, tooth loss and infection) and minimise intrinsic staining (white specs on teeth).</li>\r\n<li>White fillings - To rejuvenate his teeth, broken amalgam fillings were replaced with white fillings for a more natural, comfortable smile. Due to the nature of the breakdown of a lot of Wayne''s amalgam fillings, custom porcelain inlay or onlay were placed.</li>\r\n<li>Crowns - Dental crowns were placed in cases where large fillings were not an option. This was an excellent way to restore and retain Wayne''s teeth whilst also achieving a highly aesthetic appearance.</li>\r\n<li>Teeth whitening - BriteSmile whitening system was used to whiten Wayne''s teeth. Custom trays were also made to give Wayne a whitening maintenance program to take home to help sustain his whiter smile.</li>\r\n</ul>									<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/contact-us/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n								</div>\r\n								</div>', 'EPISODE 2 WAYNE', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '753', '', '', '2015-09-28 08: