(766, 1, '2015-09-10 08:12:14', '2015-09-10 08:12:14', '<strong>WHITE FILLINGS</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>KEEPING YOUR SMILE LOOKING NATURALLY BEAUTIFUL</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>What are White Fillings?</strong>\r\n\r\nWhite Fillings have become the preferred option for the treatment of cavities today.\r\n\r\nThey can also be used to replace unsightly grey amalgam or gold restorations.\r\n\r\nWhat are the advantages of white fillings?\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>White fillings offer a more natural tooth-like appearance,</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>By nature of their chemical composition, white fillings allow a more conservative approach to the restoration of decayed teeth.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>With white fillings, there is no need to remove healthy tooth structure as would be the case with the old style treatments.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>White fillings are a much improved alternative to earlier large long-term mercury fillings which, expanded and contracted with heat and cold causing the surrounding tooth structure to fracture.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>How are White Fillings fitted?</strong>\r\n\r\nInitially, a special dye is used to determine the extent of the decay. After that, it is safely removed and a whole filling bonded to the affected area.\r\n\r\nDepending on the size and extent of the decay, there are two White Fillings treatment options:\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Composite Resin Filling</strong> - A direct procedure that can be completed in a single visit by moulding a pliable material to the shape of the tooth and hardening it with a special blue light.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Indirect Porcelain Restoration</strong> - Suitable for larger broken down teeth. Also known as Inlays or Onlays, these types of fillings are precision-manufactured in a laboratory from a mould of the tooth using high grade porcelains, selected for its strength, durability and natural appearance.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'White Fillings', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '166-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-10 08:12:14', '2015-09-10 08:12:14', '', 166, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/166-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(767, 1, '2015-09-28 07:07:13', '2015-09-28 07:07:13', '<div class="inn_contant">\n<h3>REFRESHING YOUR BEAUTY WITHOUT BARELY NOTICING IT</h3>\n\nThough certain injectable products are commonly known and used for smoothening facial wrinkles, some of them have also found very important clinical applications in the treatment of Temporomandibular Joint Syndrome and Bruxism (teeth grinding).\n\n<h4>What is Temporomandibular Joint Syndrome?</h4>\n\nThe Temporomandibular Joint (TMJ) is the joint that connects the jaw to the skull. When we talk about Temporomandibular Joint Syndrome, we are referring to the pain and dysfunction of the muscles used in the mastication process and the temporomandibular joints which, causes dizziness and headaches.\n\nFortunately, TMJ is now treatable with a range of non-surgical procedures that inject a solution into certain muscles of the head and neck areas to leave them relaxed and pain-free.\n\nThe injectable treatment for TMJ therapy does not affect any other parts of the patient''s body other than those injected. However, depending on the severity of the headaches, additional injections may be applied to other parts of the head and neck area. Dr Yassmin will advise patients accordingly before proceeding with TMJ treatment.\n\nTMJ treatments are just one of the many Injectable treatments available at Broadway Dental Sydney to help you restore your natural beauty without barely noticing it.\n\n\n<h4>Injectable treatments can also be used in the following cases:</h4>\n<ul>\n	<li>To complement aesthetic dentistry procedures,</li>\n	<li>As a minimally invasive alternative to surgically treating high lip line cases (gummy smiles),</li>\n	<li>To correct downturn smile,</li>\n	<li>For Lip augmentation procedures, and</li>\n	<li>In some orthodontic cases where facial muscles need to be retrained.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Injectable Treatments', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '237-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-28 07:07:13', '2015-09-28 07:07:13', '', 237, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/237-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
