(769, 1, '2015-09-10 08:26:43', '2015-09-10 08:26:43', '<div class="inn_page_right">\r\n<div class="row inn_page_tytle">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<h2 class="inn_title"><span>Invisalign</span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row inn_vide">\r\n<div class="col-md-8 ">\r\n<img src="images/video_img.png" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" />\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4 inn_page_invs">\r\n<img src="images/invs_img.jpg" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive" />\r\n<h3>THE CLEAR WAY <br>\r\nTO A PERFECTLY <br>\r\nSTRAIGHT SMILE <br>\r\nINVISALIGN</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row inn_contant">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<p>To find our more about Invisalign (invisable braces) book an appointment with <a href="#">Dr. Fadi Yassmin </a>at Broadway Dental today!</p>\r\n<h3>THE SMILE YOUâ€™VE ALWAYS DREAMED OF WITH INVISALIGN</h3>\r\n<p>Have you been hiding your smile because you fear othersâ€™ negative reactions? Are you not confident about the way your teeth look? If youâ€™d like a straighter, more beautiful smile without going through traditional orthodontic treatments, Invisalign may be the answer for you.</p>\r\n<h4>What is Invisalign?</h4>\r\n<p>Invisalign is a revolutionary cosmetic dental treatment that uses a series of removable clear aligners (or invisible braces) to gradually straighten your teeth.\r\nIt is a far more comfortable and a lot less intrusive method than traditional orthodontic treatments. With Invisalign, you can achieve the smile of your dreams without anyone noticing youâ€™re undergoing a dental treatment.</p>\r\n<h4>What are the benefits of Invisalign?</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul class="list-inline">\r\n\r\n\r\n<li>Invisalign is ideal for those who have always wanted a better smile but have been putting off orthodontic treatments because of the social stigma associated with braces.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>The durable, transparent thermoplastic material of the Invisalign aligners make them almost impossible to see and as such, a much more discreet alternative to orthodontic treatments.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Being completely removable, it is easy to maintain the daily oral hygiene routine needed to reduce the chance of plaque build-up, tooth decay and gum disease.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>These invisible braces donâ€™t rely on traditional metal appliances, so food and plaque are not trapped on the surface of the teeth.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>It is a surprisingly fast treatment, with most of our patients requiring approximately less than a year to transform their smile and be able to display their beautiful new look.</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>YOUR INVISALIGN TREATMENT</h2>\r\n<p>During your initial consultation at Broadway Dentalâ€™s Sydney Clinic, Dr Yassmin will gain an understanding of your current situation, and explore your goals to determine if Invisalign is suitable for you. Should this be the case, Dr Yassmin will then begin by taking detailed impressions of your teeth. These will then be digitised to create a computerised 3D image of your smile from which, Dr Yassmin will be able to determine the precise movements needed to create the best results. Subsequently, your custom-made invisible braces will be crafted according to your individual treatment plan.\r\nThe number of aligners you will need will depend on your needs and goals however, a full Invisalign treatment typically involves the use of 18 to 36 aligners, and it takes around 9 to 18 months.</p>\r\n<h2>LIVING WITH INVISALIGN</h2>\r\n<p>During your treatment, you will wear each aligner for around two weeks, day and night, with small breaks for eating, brushing and flossing your teeth, and the occasional time off for special events. After two weeks, you will then switch to the next aligner which, will move your teeth a little more.\r\nWe will ask you to come in for a check-up every 4-6 weeks so that we can monitor your progress and provide you with your next set of aligners.\r\nThroughout your treatment, you should notice small movements as the invisible braces gradually move your teeth to create an even, healthy and very attractive smile.\r\nTo find out how Invisalign can help you achieve a Hollywood smile, call us today on (02) 9281 0100 or via email.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Invisalign', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-10 08:26:43', '2015-09-10 08:26:43', '', 95, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
