yÂ consistent,Â controlledÂ forceÂ toÂ individualÂ teeth,Â gentlyÂ movingÂ themÂ intoÂ theirÂ newÂ desiredÂ position.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nInvisalignÂ differsÂ fromÂ traditionalÂ bracesÂ inÂ thatÂ itÂ actuallyÂ controlsÂ theÂ amountÂ ofÂ forceÂ appliedÂ toÂ eachÂ toothÂ andÂ thisÂ reducesÂ theÂ lengthÂ ofÂ theÂ treatmentÂ inÂ comparisonÂ withÂ traditionalÂ orthodontics.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHowÂ effectiveÂ isÂ Invisalign?\r\n\r\n\r\nStudiesÂ showÂ thatÂ outÂ ofÂ theÂ 1.5Â millionÂ peopleÂ whoÂ haveÂ hadÂ orÂ areÂ havingÂ InvisalignÂ treatment,Â 98%Â ofÂ themÂ areÂ satisfiedÂ withÂ theÂ results.\r\n\r\n\r\nHowever,Â it''sÂ importantÂ toÂ rememberÂ thatÂ InvisalignÂ cannotÂ treatÂ allÂ orthodonticÂ conditionsÂ suchÂ asÂ severeÂ overÂ orÂ underbites,Â severelyÂ tippedÂ teeth,Â numerousÂ missingÂ teeth,Â orÂ uneruptedÂ teeth.\r\n\r\n\r\nToÂ findÂ outÂ whetherÂ InvisalignÂ isÂ rightÂ forÂ you,Â talkÂ toÂ theÂ teamÂ atÂ BroadwayÂ DentalÂ onÂ (02)Â 9281Â 0100Â orÂ viaÂ email.\r\n\r\nWhatÂ doesÂ InvisalignÂ lookÂ like?\r\n\r\n\r\nTheÂ clear,Â strong,Â non-toxicÂ plasticÂ materialÂ InvisalignÂ alignersÂ areÂ manufacturedÂ with,Â makeÂ themÂ veryÂ difficultÂ toÂ seeÂ whenÂ worn.Â Besides,Â havingÂ beenÂ custom-madeÂ specificallyÂ forÂ eachÂ patientÂ accordingÂ toÂ theirÂ treatmentÂ plan,Â alignersÂ fitÂ veryÂ neatlyÂ toÂ theÂ teeth.\r\n\r\n\r\nHowÂ longÂ doesÂ InvisalignÂ treatmentÂ take?\r\n\r\n\r\nTreatmentÂ timesÂ varyÂ butÂ onÂ average,Â patientsÂ achieveÂ straighterÂ teethÂ withÂ InvisalignÂ inÂ aroundÂ twelveÂ toÂ fourteenÂ months,Â fourÂ monthsÂ lessÂ thanÂ traditionalÂ braces.\r\n\r\n\r\nIsÂ InvisalignÂ painful?\r\n\r\nWearingÂ theÂ InvisalignÂ alignersÂ isÂ generallyÂ farÂ moreÂ comfortableÂ thanÂ wearingÂ traditionalÂ braces.Â MinorÂ discomfortÂ mayÂ beÂ experiencedÂ initiallyÂ andÂ forÂ aÂ fewÂ daysÂ everyÂ timeÂ aÂ newÂ alignerÂ isÂ used.Â ThisÂ slightÂ feelingÂ ofÂ pressureÂ isÂ aÂ signÂ alignersÂ areÂ doingÂ theirÂ jobÂ andÂ movingÂ theÂ teethÂ intoÂ theÂ desiredÂ position.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAnyÂ discomfortÂ isÂ usuallyÂ relievedÂ inÂ aÂ fewÂ days.\r\n\r\n\r\nHowÂ muchÂ doesÂ InvisalignÂ cost?\r\n\r\n\r\nTheÂ costÂ ofÂ anÂ InvisalignÂ treatmentÂ dependsÂ onÂ individualÂ circumstancesÂ butÂ forÂ mostÂ ofÂ ourÂ patientsÂ atÂ BroadwayÂ Dental,Â theÂ costÂ ofÂ aÂ fullÂ treatmentÂ rangesÂ betweenÂ $3000Â andÂ $10,000.\r\n\r\n\r\nAfterÂ ourÂ initialÂ consultationÂ we''llÂ beÂ ableÂ toÂ provideÂ youÂ withÂ aÂ treatmentÂ planÂ detailingÂ allÂ costsÂ forÂ yourÂ specificÂ needs.\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Invisalign', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-10 08:50:30', '2015-09-10 08:50:30', '', 95, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
