ass="blur"></div>\r\n							<div class="caption-text">\r\n								<h3 style=" border-bottom: 1px solid #005756;\r\n    border-top: 2px solid #005756;\r\n    font-size: 20px;\r\n    padding: 5px 10px 10px;">THIS IS H3</h3>\r\n								<p>Loren ipsum dolor si amet ipsum dolor si amet ipsum dolor...</p>\r\n								<a class="btn btn-success" href="#"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus"> INFO</span></a>\r\n							</div>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				\r\n	    </div>\r\n        \r\n\r\n<div class="col-md-9">\r\n<h2>Offering Cosmetic Dentistry, Teeth Whitening, Sleep Dentistry, Smile Makeovers and Dental Implants.</h2>\r\n<h4>ABOUT BROADWAY DENTAL</h4>\r\nUp until now, many patients have associated dental care with cold, clinical environments and painful treatments, but those negative connotations are now a thing of the past. Broadway Dental has revolutionised the way patients feel about their dentists and their regular dental visits. Since their establishment in 1998, Broadway Dental has been providing Sydney residents with a more effective - and more pleasant -- alternative to traditional dental care. For nearly two decades, Broadway Dental has remained at the forefront of general and cosmetic dental treatments and all oral health care solutions.\r\n\r\nAll-On-4 implant is just one example of our technological innovation and our commitment to quality service. Our All-On-4 implant combines the stability of a fixed bridge with the comfort and convenience of a dental implant.\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental, we are proud to offer a wide range of cosmetic dentistry procedures, including Teeth Whitening, Sleep Dentistry, Dental Implants, Invisalign, White Fillings, Porcelain Veneers, and many others. No matter what your smile needs, Broadway Dental guarantees:\r\n<ul class="list-inline">\r\n	<li>A personalised approach to long-term dental care,</li>\r\n	<li>Pain-free, professional dental treatments,</li>\r\n	<li>State-of-the art equipment,</li>\r\n	<li>The latest advances in cosmetic dentistry,</li>\r\n	<li>And a boutique environment conveniently located in the Sydney CBD.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>A comfortable, serene environment</h4>\r\nThoughtfully designed by Dr Fadi Yassmin himself, the warm and serene ambiance of the centre is designed to help all patients feel relaxed and at ease. We want you to look forward to your dental visits - and we work hard to make that happen.\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-12">\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>A personalised approach to dental care</h4>\r\nIn the comfortable and tranquil environment of our boutique-style clinic, we discuss our patients'' oral health goals and customise a personalised dental health plan that matches their specific needs and requirements.\r\nAt Broadway Dental we do not believe in the one-size-fits-all approach to dental care. We know that every patient is unique, and we want every patient who walks through our doors to leave happy and satisfied with their new whiter and brighter smiles.\r\n<h4>State-of-the art equipment</h4>\r\nCommitted to continually invest and upgrade the centreâ€™s advanced equipment, Dr Yassmin and his team are able to perform an extensive range of cosmetic dentistry procedures to provide the kind of healthy, beautiful smile their patients are looking for.\r\n<h4>Latest techniques in pain-free dentistry</h4>\r\nAt Broadway Dental, we want your visit to be positive and pain-free. We use the latest technology and take advantage of all advances in cosmetic dentistry procedures to provide services that are absolutely pain-free and non-invasive. Dr Yassmin and his team are able to deliver restorative and cosmetic dentistry to correct, restore, enhance and maintain your smile - all without the pain and fear often associated with a trip to the dentist.\r\nAt Broadway Dental, our state-of-the-art sleep dentistry is administered by a highly qualified Sydney anaesthetist who works alongside Dr Yassmin. Our sleep dentistry is also available for those patients who are particularly apprehensive about dental procedures, and those who will be undergoing long-term procedures.\r\n<h4>An outstanding team of dental care practitioners</h4>\r\nCommitted to undergo continuous professional development in order to provide the highest standards of dentistry, Dr Fadi Yassmin regularly attends advanced training at a number of leading dental institutes, including the renowned Kings College, the Australian Academy of Dento-Facial Aesthetics and, UCLA â€“ one of the worldâ€™s leading medical centres.\r\nDr. Fadi Yassmin is also committed to the QIP approach to dental practice. The initials QIP stand for Quality - Innovation - Performance - and those three commitments are at the heart of everything we do at Broadway Dental. The QIP standard is the result of a collaboration with the Australian Dental Association (ADA), and it serves as further reassurance that patients are in safe and capable hands.\r\nQIP dental practices are committed to the high standards of the National Safety and Quality Health Service (NSQHS) Standards, and Dr. Fadi Yassmin and his team are proud to uphold those high standards.\r\n\r\nTo find out more about us, call us on 02-92810100 or click here to book and appointment online. \r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 00:24:59', '2015-09-11 00:24:59', '', 9, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/9-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
