(804, 1, '2015-09-11 01:30:11', '2015-09-11 01:30:11', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>KEEPING YOUR SMILE LOOKING NATURALLY BEAUTIFUL</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>What are White Fillings?</h4>\r\n\r\nWhite Fillings have become the preferred option for the treatment of cavities today.\r\n\r\nThey can also be used to replace unsightly grey amalgam or gold restorations.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<h4>What are the advantages of white fillings?</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>White fillings offer a more natural tooth-like appearance,</li>\r\n	<li>By nature of their chemical composition, white fillings allow a more conservative approach to the restoration of decayed teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>With white fillings, there is no need to remove healthy tooth structure as would be the case with the old style treatments.</li>\r\n	<li>White fillings are a much improved alternative to earlier large long-term mercury fillings which, expanded and contracted with heat and cold causing the surrounding tooth structure to fracture.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>How are White Fillings fitted?</h4>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nInitially, a special dye is used to determine the extent of the decay. After that, it is safely removed and a whole filling bonded to the affected area.\r\n\r\n<h4>Depending on the size and extent of the decay, there are two White Fillings treatment options:</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Composite Resin Filling</strong> - A direct procedure that can be completed in a single visit by moulding a pliable material to the shape of the tooth and hardening it with a special blue light.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Indirect Porcelain Restoration</strong> - Suitable for larger broken down teeth. Also known as Inlays or Onlays, these types of fillings are precision-manufactured in a laboratory from a mould of the tooth using high grade porcelains, selected for its strength, durability and natural appearance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'White Fillings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'white-fillings', '', '', '2015-09-28 07:06:55', '2015-09-28 07:06:55', '', 11, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=804', 0, 'page', '', 0),
