(806, 1, '2015-09-11 01:30:55', '2015-09-11 01:30:55', '<div class="crown-text">\r\n			\r\n			<div>\r\n				<p>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME - DENTAL CROWNS</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Living with the stigma of a broken tooth?</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>You don''t have to.</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Not with the very natural-looking Dental Crowns available from Broadway Dental.</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Dental Crowns (or caps) are designed to cover or ''cap'' a tooth to restore it to its normal shape and size, strengthening and improving its appearance.</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>Visit us at Broadway Dental to find out about Dental Crowns and you too, could be on your way to sharing an A-list smile with the rest of the world!</p>\r\n\r\n			</div>\r\n </div>', 'Dental Crowns', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '168-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 01:30:55', '2015-09-11 01:30:55', '', 168, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/168-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(807, 1, '2015-09-11 01:32:18', '2015-09-11 01:32:18', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>RESTORE YOUR ORAL HEALTH AND REGAIN YOUR SMILE AND CONFIDENCE</h3>\r\n<p>Facing the world with missing teeth is not easy and it leads to consequences much beyond the obvious difficulties eating or speaking.</p>\r\n<p>Missing teeth has severe negative psychological effects including a very serious lack of self-confidence in social and professional situations.</p>\r\n<p>Dental Implants can and will help you regain your ability to interact socially with confidence.</p>\r\n<h4>What are Dental Implants? </h4>\r\n<p>A Dental Implant is an artificial tooth root that is submerged into the jawbone.</p>\r\n<p>Manufactured from an extremely strong, biocompatible titanium, Dental Implants bind with the bone in a process called â€˜osseointegrationâ€™ which, effectively cements the implant into the jaw. Neighbouring teeth also benefit from this procedure, and chances of avoiding gum disease, teeth shifting, and premature tooth wear improve dramatically as well.</p>\r\n<p>Dental Implants are a much more comfortable and natural option than traditional dentures and aesthetically, they do resemble a normal tooth root.</p>\r\n<h4>When should Dental Implants be used? </h4>\r\n<p>Whether you are missing one tooth, several teeth, or all your teeth, Dental Implants are the perfect treatment to help you regain that gorgeous smile again.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Using some of the most advanced dental techniques available to patients today, Dental Implants can be used to:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Restore one or more missing teeth.</strong><br>\r\nThe team at Broadway Dental can replace a single tooth using one implant and a crown. The dental implant replaces both your tooth and its root, forming a very secure restoration that does not affect your bordering teeth.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Anchor a dental bridge. </strong><br>\r\nIf you are living with several missing teeth, a dental bridge secured by implants can do away with the need for a removable, partial denture.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Support a full denture.</strong><br>\r\nIf you are missing all of your teeth, dentures supported by implants are a far more secure and comfortable option, helping you to chew and speak more naturally than with traditional dentures.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>YOUR DENTAL IMPLANT TREATMENT</h4>\r\n<p>Your journey towards regaining a complete smile begins with a personal consultation with Dr Yassmin at our Sydney based dental clinic, to determine whether dental implants are the right option for you. If together we decide to proceed, the next step is implant placement surgery.</p>\r\n<p>Usually under local anaesthetics, the tooth implant is gently eased into your jaw bone through a tiny incision in your gum. You then take a break from treatment for around three months, to allow the implant to securely integrate with your bone.</p>\r\n<p>Between three and six months later, we invite you to return to Broadway Dental Sydney to have your new tooth restoration fitted. Once this dental crown or bridge is placed on your implant, your tooth replacement is complete, and you can enjoy the feeling of a smile which is whole, healthy, and attractive once again.</p>\r\n<h4>DENTAL IMPLANTS VERSUS DENTURES OR A BRIDGE</h4>\r\n<p><strong>Dental implants offer many advantages over more traditional restorations such as dentures or dental bridges, including:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>An enviable rate of success guaranteed by their highly predictable results,</li>\r\n<li>Once inserted, dental implants look and function exactly like your natural teeth. Because they securely integrate with your jawbone, implants help to prevent bone loss and receding gums, which are often an unwanted by-product of dentures and bridges.</li>\r\n<li>Unlike dental bridges, implants donâ€™t need your neighbouring healthy teeth to be altered in any way to provide support. With your healthy tooth enamel remaining untouched, you can experience much better oral health over the long term.</li>\r\n<li>Dental Implants can help you speak, chew and live normally once more, without having to ever worry about loose, ill-fitting dentures.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>You wonâ€™t believe the feeling of self-confidence and comfort youâ€™ll experience, all thanks to Dental Implants!</p>\r\n<h3>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h3>\r\n\r\n[su_accordion]\r\n  \r\n  [su_spoiler title="Q. Are Dental Implants right for me?" style="fancy"] A.<strong> Dental Implants are a suitable treatment for most patients as long as:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>They enjoy good oral and overall health,</li>\r\n<li>Have sufficient bone in the jaw to properly support an implant and,</li>\r\n<li>Do not suffer from gum disease.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSpeak to the Broadway Dental team to arrange your personalised consultation and find out whether you are eligible to have Dental Implants by calling (02) 9281 0100 or via email. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[su_spoiler title="Q. What do dental implants look like?" style="fancy"] A. The Dental Implants themselves resemble tiny titanium screws which, are surgically implanted into your jaw bone. Once these titanium foundations have fully integrated with your bone, Dr Yassmin will place a natural-looking tooth coloured crown to fully restore the appearance and function of your tooth. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[su_spoiler title="Q. How long does a Dental Implant treatment take?" style="fancy"] A. If you enjoy good oral health and you have sufficient jaw bone to work with, Dr Yassmin will be able to start on your dental implant treatment straight away. If you need bone grafting, this extra procedure will take around three months before your tooth implant placement can begin.\r\n\r\nIn most cases, two appointments are all thatâ€™s needed to complete a full Dental Implant treatment. During your first appointment, the expert team of cosmetic dentists at Broadway Sydney will surgically place your implant. Three to six months later, at your second appointment, theyâ€™ll restore your tooth with a dental crown. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[su_spoiler title="Q. How will I look after my Dental Implants?" style="fancy"] A. Just like your natural teeth, dental implants need a meticulous at-home oral hygiene routine and regular visits to our Sydney dental clinic for a long-lasting good health.\r\n\r\nYou should continue to brush thoroughly twice a day, floss once a day, and attend twice-yearly check-ups with Dr Yassmin to ensure your overall oral health. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[su_spoiler title="Q. How long can I expect my Dental Implant to last?" style="fancy"] A. With proper care and regular follow up appointments with Broadway Dental, dental implants can last a lifetime.\r\n\r\nPlease note: Any surgical or invasive procedure carries a certain risk. Before proceeding, we advise you to seek a second opinion from an appropriately qualified oral health practitioner. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[/su_accordion]\r\n\r\n\r\n     \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n																			<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="#">book your consultation today</a>\r\n																												<a title="Dental Implants Sydney Cases" class="book-now" href="#">our dental implants success stories</a>\r\n																										</div>', 'Dental Implants', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dental-implants', '', '', '2015-09-16 04:06:32', '2015-09-16 04:06:32', '', 11, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?page_id=807', 0, 'page', '', 0),
