(876, 1, '2015-09-11 02:33:25', '2015-09-11 02:33:25', '<h2>TEETH WHITENING</h2>\r\n<h2>ENJOY A BEAUTIFUL, WHITER SMILE WITH TEETH WHITENING</h2>\r\n\r\nDo you get the feeling your teeth are obstructing success in your personal and professional lives?\r\n\r\nWhile regular dental care at home can help prevent some oral diseases, the effect of a number of external agents like red wine, tea or coffee - or the more serious habit of smoking - can stain your teeth and dull your smile over the years.\r\n\r\nSydney''s leading cosmetic dentist, Dr Fadi Yassmin, will draw a brand new smile for you with his range of Teeth Whitening treatments. In fact, you probably won''t believe how quickly you''ll be able to enjoy a naturally white smile, and the tremendous self-confidence boost that comes with it!\r\n\r\n<h2>HOW EFFECTIVE IS TOOTH WHITENING?</h2>\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental we offer two types of Teeth Whitening treatments, both equally effective and safe - In-chair whitening and At-home whitening.\r\n\r\nWhile both have been clinically tested and proven to remove deep teeth stains, their level of success will depend on the condition of the patient''s teeth, the type of staining, and the specific method of Teeth Whitening treatment chosen.\r\n\r\nTo maximise results, Dr Yassmin will advise the best whitening method for your needs.\r\n\r\n<h2>IN-CHAIR TEETH WHITENING</h2>\r\n\r\nIf this is your preferred option, the Broadway Dental team will have your unsightly stains removed in just a single appointment.\r\n\r\nThat''s right.\r\n\r\nOne visit to your favourite boutique dental studio is all it takes to have your teeth up to 12 shades lighter!\r\n\r\nWhat does In-chair Teeth Whitening involve?\r\n\r\nDr Yassmin will apply an advanced light-activated teeth whitening gel and leave it to do its job for approximately 90 minutes.\r\n\r\nDepending on the shade of your teeth and the results you wish to accomplish, this application will be repeated two or three times more.\r\n\r\nIn just under an hour, your teeth colour will be up to 12 shades lighter, and your smile will be sure to make an impression wherever you go!\r\n\r\nPlus, to complement your In-chair whitening treatment, Broadway Dental will provide you with a take-home touch up kit to maintain your beautiful, whiter new smile.\r\n\r\nAll our whitening products have been specially selected to minimise tooth sensitivity during treatment, to ensure our patients are fully comfortable while they are having the appearance of their teeth radically improved.\r\n\r\n<h2>PROFESSIONAL AT-HOME TEETH WHITENING</h2>\r\n\r\nThis is the ideal Teeth Whitening treatment if you prefer to achieve a whiter new smile in the comfort of your very own home.\r\n\r\nYour At-home Teeth Whitening treatment will effectively remove deep stains from your teeth to almost the same extent as our In-chair whitening - it''ll just take slightly longer to achieve the same results.\r\n\r\nWhat does At-Home Teeth Whitening involve?\r\n\r\nThe team at Broadway Dental will provide you with a take-home whitening kit that comprises a custom-fitted tray and a whitening gel. All you need to do is fill the tray it with the gel and wear it for the prescribed amount of time.\r\n\r\nIn just over about two weeks, you''ll notice your smile becoming gradually lighter as the stains in your teeth begin to fade away.\r\n\r\nTo find out if Teeth Whitening could improve your smile, and to discuss which treatment would best suit you, contact the Broadway Dental Sydney team today on (02) 9281 0100 or via email.\r\n\r\n<h2>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h2>\r\n\r\nIs a teeth whitening treatment suitable for me?\r\n\r\nIf you have healthy teeth and gums, and you do not suffer from overly sensitive teeth or receding gums, Teeth Whitening may be the ideal way to remove stains and freshen up your smile.\r\n\r\nThe best way to find out if your teeth could benefit from whitening is to book a personalised assessment with Dr Yassmin and the Broadway Dental team on (02) 9281 0100 or via email.\r\n\r\n<h2>How much does Teeth Whitening cost?</h2>\r\n\r\nThe cost of your Teeth Whitening treatment will vary depending on the method you opt for.\r\n\r\nAt-home Teeth Whitening costs approximately $550, while an instant In-chair Teeth Whitening in the comfort of Broadway''s Dental clinic will be $995 (including a take home whitening kit).\r\n\r\n<h2>How safe are Teeth Whitening treatments?</h2>\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental we only use whitening treatments which have undergone extensive clinical testing to ensure your absolute comfort and safety.\r\n\r\nTo determine the right treatment option, we will first conduct a thorough oral examination to determine if teeth whitening could be of benefit to you, and then provide advice on the best treatment method for your needs.\r\n\r\n<h2>How long does Teeth Whitening last?</h2>\r\n\r\nThe duration of your Teeth Whitening treatment will depend on a number of lifestyle choices you make after your treatment. Consuming tea, coffee or red wine regularly will cause your teeth to stain quicker than if you were to reduce their intake.\r\n\r\nSmoking is another bad habit which, we strongly advise you to give up. Not only does it cause the unsightly staining of your teeth, it can also lead to serious problems for your oral and overall health.\r\n\r\nThe good news is it will take just as long to stain your teeth again as it did in the first place, so by maintaining good habits and excellent oral hygiene you can extend the results of your whitening treatment.\r\n\r\nTo find out more about teeth whitening service, call us on 02-92810100 or click here to book an appointment online.', 'Teeth Whitening', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '809-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 02:33:25', '2015-09-11 02:33:25', '', 809, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/809-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
