(949, 1, '2015-09-14 00:14:23', '2015-09-14 00:14:23', '<h4>Throw away your old dentures</h4>\n\nFor many people dentures are cumbersome, uncomfortable and constantly loose, making them feel uneasy about smiling and eating, while missing teeth can compromise on your oral and general health.\n<h2>WHY ALL ON 4?</h2>\nThere are many benefits to choosing the All-On-4 System. Some include:\n<ul>\n	<li>They look, feel and function just like natural teeth</li>\n	<li>Aid in helping to keep your jaw bone strong</li>\n	<li>Virtually eliminates the need for bone grafting, which is invasive, and adds to recovery time</li>\n	<li>Easy to clean and maintain good oral health</li>\n	<li>Less expensive than traditional dental implants as fewer implants are required.</li>\n</ul>\nThe All-On-4 System from Broadway Dental can give you a complete smile once again and help you regain your confidence. Unlike a denture which is held by adhesive and a bridge, which relies on healthy teeth for support, the All-On-4 System of prosthetics is permanently secured with dental implants.', 'Benifits of All on 4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 00:14:23', '2015-09-14 00:14:23', '', 133, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/133-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(950, 1, '2015-09-11 07:28:19', '2015-09-11 07:28:19', 'Throw away your old dentures\r\n\r\nFor many people dentures are cumbersome, uncomfortable and constantly loose, making them feel uneasy about smiling and eating, while missing teeth can compromise on your oral and general health.\r\n<h2>WHY ALL ON 4?</h2>\r\nThere are many benefits to choosing the All-On-4 System. Some include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>They look, feel and function just like natural teeth</li>\r\n	<li>Aid in helping to keep your jaw bone strong</li>\r\n	<li>Virtually eliminates the need for bone grafting, which is invasive, and adds to recovery time</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to clean and maintain good oral health</li>\r\n	<li>Less expensive than traditional dental implants as fewer implants are required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe All-On-4 System from Broadway Dental can give you a complete smile once again and help you regain your confidence. Unlike a denture which is held by adhesive and a bridge, which relies on healthy teeth for support, the All-On-4 System of prosthetics is permanently secured with dental implants.', 'Benifits of All on 4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 07:28:19', '2015-09-11 07:28:19', '', 133, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/133-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
