(951, 1, '2015-09-11 08:17:57', '2015-09-11 08:17:57', '<h2>WHATÂ ISÂ ALLÂ ONÂ 4Â DENTALÂ IMPLANT</h2>\n\nWhatÂ isÂ AllÂ OnÂ 4Â dentalÂ implant?\n\nTheÂ All-On-4Â systemÂ offeredÂ atÂ BroadwayÂ DentalÂ representsÂ theÂ stateÂ ofÂ theÂ artÂ inÂ implantÂ dentistry,Â whichÂ bringsÂ aÂ dentalÂ prosthesisÂ andÂ dentalÂ implantsÂ together.</p>\nAÂ dentalÂ implantÂ isÂ aÂ fineÂ titaniumÂ screwÂ orÂ rodÂ placedÂ intoÂ theÂ jawÂ boneÂ duringÂ aÂ minorÂ surgicalÂ procedureÂ toÂ replaceÂ aÂ missingÂ toothÂ root.Â TitaniumÂ isÂ aÂ strongÂ bio-compatibleÂ alloyÂ andÂ hasÂ beenÂ usedÂ successfullyÂ inÂ reconstructiveÂ medicineÂ forÂ manyÂ yearsÂ asÂ itÂ naturallyÂ integratesÂ withÂ bone.\nPreviously,Â aÂ singleÂ dentalÂ implantÂ wasÂ placedÂ verticallyÂ andÂ usedÂ toÂ replaceÂ aÂ singleÂ toothÂ orÂ supportÂ aÂ dentalÂ bridgeÂ ofÂ upÂ toÂ threeÂ teeth.Â ToÂ supportÂ anÂ entireÂ upperÂ orÂ lowerÂ archÂ ofÂ teeth,Â upÂ toÂ eightÂ dentalÂ implantsÂ wereÂ necessary.</\n<p>TheÂ All-On-4Â SystemÂ enablesÂ youÂ toÂ haveÂ aÂ setÂ ofÂ upperÂ orÂ lowerÂ prostheticÂ teethÂ permanentlyÂ secured,Â oftenÂ withÂ asÂ fewÂ asÂ fourÂ dentalÂ implants.</p>\n<p>TheÂ treatmentÂ isÂ madeÂ possibleÂ becauseÂ twoÂ ofÂ theÂ implantsÂ areÂ slightlyÂ longerÂ thanÂ traditionalÂ dentalÂ implants.Â TheyÂ areÂ alsoÂ placedÂ atÂ anÂ acuteÂ angleÂ atÂ theÂ frontÂ ofÂ theÂ mouthÂ whereÂ yourÂ jawÂ boneÂ isÂ denserÂ andÂ stronger,Â andÂ providesÂ theÂ greatestÂ supportÂ forÂ yourÂ prosthesis.</p>', 'All on 4 Procedure', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '137-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 08:17:57', '2015-09-11 08:17:57', '', 137, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/137-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
