(966, 1, '2015-09-11 08:53:39', '2015-09-11 08:53:39', '<h3>RESTORING SMILE WITH ALL ON 4 PROCEDURE</h3>\r\nIf you have loose and uncomfortable removable dentures, have a bridge, are losing or missing teeth, All-On-4 may be the perfect permanent restorative solution for your smile.\r\n\r\nÂ \r\n\r\nThe All-On-4 System available at Broadway Dental allows you to replace your removable dentures or missing teeth with a permanently secured prosthesis.\r\n\r\nÂ \r\n\r\nOne of the main advantages of the All-On-4 System, is only a very small percentage of people are unsuitable for this procedure. If you no-longer wish to wear loose and uncomfortable dentures, have been told you''re unsuitable for dental implants, are missing teeth or want a permanent bridge replacement, then the All-on-4 System may be the perfect restorative solution for you.\r\n\r\nÂ \r\n\r\nDr Fadi Yassmin is a leading authority on implant dentistry. Many patients come to, or are referred to Dr Yassmin and the team at Broadway Dental for assessment and advice on the best treatment options to restore their smile through the All-On-4 System.\r\n\r\nÂ \r\n\r\nThe All-On-4 System lets you enjoy all the benefits of having a full upper and lower arch of permanently secured prosthetic teeth and a healthy, perfect smile.', 'All on 4 Procedure', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '137-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 08:53:39', '2015-09-11 08:53:39', '', 137, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/137-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
