(972, 1, '2015-09-11 10:10:20', '2015-09-11 10:10:20', 'CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ ORTHODONTICS\r\n\r\nConcerned about the kind of effect your smile is having on your personal and professional life?\r\nUnderstandably so.\r\n\r\nYour smile has a dramatic effect on the way others react towards you, and most importantly on your self-esteem.\r\n\r\nSo, if you want to start making a better impression with a dashing smile, itâ€™s time to talk to Dr Yassmin about Orthodontic Treatments.\r\n\r\nWhat are Orthodontic Treatments?\r\n\r\nWhile initially designed to treat misaligned teeth in pre-teens and teens, today many adults are choosing to undergo orthodontics to help them achieve that beautiful straight smile they have always wanted but never had an opportunity to correct in their younger years.\r\n\r\nWhat are the benefits of Orthodontics?\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Improve patientsâ€™ smile/self-confidence,</li>\r\n<li>Improve the width of the dental arches,</li>\r\n<li>Influence growth of the jaws to the ideal position,</li>\r\n<li>Reduce or eliminate the need to extract permanent teeth,</li>\r\n<li>Lower the risk of injury to protruded front teeth,</li>\r\n<li> Reduce the likelihood of impacted permanent teeth,</li>\r\n<li>Correct oral habits,</li>\r\n <li>Reduce appearance-consciousness during critical developmental years.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Orthodontics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '180-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:10:20', '2015-09-11 10:10:20', '', 180, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/180-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(973, 1, '2015-09-11 10:12:09', '2015-09-11 10:12:09', '<h4>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ DENTAL VENEERS</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you get the feeling people judge you on your smile?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A gorgeous smile will open new doors for you, improve your confidence, your personal relationships, and your ability to communicate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now you can achieve the smile you always wanted with Porcelain Veneers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What are Porcelain Veneers?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Constructed from strong, high quality porcelains that closely mimic the many shades and translucencies found in natural teeth, each Dental Veneer consists of a thin porcelain shell which fits perfectly well over the front surfaces of your teeth. Once in position, veneers can help create a flawless smile, specifically designed to match your preferred look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether to hide minor chips or cracks to teeth, misaligned teeth, gaps, irregularly shaped teeth or whether to give a fresh new look to your discoloured or stained teeth, Dental Veneers are an excellent way to help improve your smile.</p>\r\n', 'Dental Venners', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:12:09', '2015-09-11 10:12:09', '', 264, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
