(979, 1, '2015-09-11 10:24:54', '2015-09-11 10:24:54', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h4>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ DENTAL IMPLANTS</h4>\r\n\r\nFacing the world with missing teeth may have severe negative psychological consequences that extend much beyond the mere difficulties eating or speaking. Missing teeth may lead to a very damaging lack of self-confidence in social and professional situations.\r\n\r\nDental Implants can help you regain the ability to interact socially with confidence.\r\n\r\nAn extremely strong artificial tooth root that is submerged into the jawbone, dental implants are a much more comfortable and natural option than traditional dentures and aesthetically, they do resemble a normal tooth root.\r\n\r\nSo, whether you need to restore one or more missing teeth, anchor a dental bridge or support a full denture, dental implants might be the right option for you.\r\n\r\nLet Dr Yassmin and his team at Broadway Dental assess whether dental implants are the perfect treatment to give you a smile which is whole, healthy, and attractive once again.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Dental Implants', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '129-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:24:54', '2015-09-11 10:24:54', '', 129, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/129-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
