(984, 1, '2015-09-11 10:27:54', '2015-09-11 10:27:54', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h4>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ GUM LIFT</h4>\r\n\r\n<strong>Have you always felt conscious about your â€œgummyâ€ smile?</strong>\r\n\r\nA Gum Lift performed by Dr Yassmin and his team of dental experts at Broadway Dental can improve the appearance of your smile and help you improve your level of self-confidence.\r\n\r\nThis simple surgical procedure consists in reshaping your upper gums â€“ generally the most visible part of your mouth to others when you smile-, resulting in a fuller and more aesthetically pleasing smile.\r\n\r\nA gum lift procedure is usually performed in one single visit and healing is in most cases very quick. In approximately 12 weeks, you could be having your gums perfectly repositioned to dazzle the world with a brand new smile!\r\n</div>\r\n', 'Gumlift', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '276-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:27:54', '2015-09-11 10:27:54', '', 276, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/276-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(985, 1, '2015-09-11 10:29:17', '2015-09-11 10:29:17', '<div class="inn_contant">\n<h4>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ ORTHODONTICS</h4>\n\nConcerned about the kind of effect your smile is having on your personal and professional life?\nUnderstandably so.\n\nYour smile has a dramatic effect on the way others react towards you, and most importantly on your self-esteem.\n\nSo, if you want to start making a better impression with a dashing smile, itâ€™s time to talk to Dr Yassmin about Orthodontic Treatments.\n\n<strong>What are Orthodontic Treatments?</strong>\n\nWhile initially designed to treat misaligned teeth in pre-teens and teens, today many adults are choosing to undergo orthodontics to help them achieve that beautiful straight smile they have always wanted but never had an opportunity to correct in their younger years.\n\n<strong>What are the benefits of Orthodontics?</strong>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Improve patientsâ€™ smile/self-confidence,</li>\n<li>Improve the width of the dental arches,</li>\n<li>Influence growth of the jaws to the ideal position,</li>\n<li>Reduce or eliminate the need to extract permanent teeth,</li>\n<li>Lower the risk of injury to protruded front teeth,</li>\n<li> Reduce the likelihood of impacted permanent teeth,</li>\n<li>Correct oral habits,</li>\n <li>Reduce appearance-consciousness during critical developmental years.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>', 'Orthodontics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '180-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:29:17', '2015-09-11 10:29:17', '', 180, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/180-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(986, 1, '2015-09-11 10:29:18', '2015-09-11 10:29:18', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h4>CREATING PERFECT SMILES ONE TOOTH AT A TIME â€“ ORTHODONTICS</h4>\r\n\r\nConcerned about the kind of effect your smile is having on your personal and professional life?\r\nUnderstandably so.\r\n\r\nYour smile has a dramatic effect on the way others react towards you, and most importantly on your self-esteem.\r\n\r\nSo, if you want to start making a better impression with a dashing smile, itâ€™s time to talk to Dr Yassmin about Orthodontic Treatments.\r\n\r\n<strong>What are Orthodontic Treatments?</strong>\r\n\r\nWhile initially designed to treat misaligned teeth in pre-teens and teens, today many adults are choosing to undergo orthodontics to help them achieve that beautiful straight smile they have always wanted but never had an opportunity to correct in their younger years.\r\n\r\n<strong>What are the benefits of Orthodontics?</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Improve patientsâ€™ smile/self-confidence,</li>\r\n<li>Improve the width of the dental arches,</li>\r\n<li>Influence growth of the jaws to the ideal position,</li>\r\n<li>Reduce or eliminate the need to extract permanent teeth,</li>\r\n<li>Lower the risk of injury to protruded front teeth,</li>\r\n<li> Reduce the likelihood of impacted permanent teeth,</li>\r\n<li>Correct oral habits,</li>\r\n <li>Reduce appearance-consciousness during critical developmental years.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Orthodontics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '180-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-11 10:29:18', '2015-09-11 10:29:18', '', 180, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/180-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(987, 1, '2015-09-14 00:07:00', '2015-09-14 00:07:00', '<div class="row inn_vide">\r\n<div class="col-md-8 "><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8XH0-kzg8jw?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;controls=1&amp;autohide=1" width="100%" height="280" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4 inn_page_invs">\r\n<div class="image-logo"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-99" src="http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/invs_img.jpg" alt="invs_img" width="200" height="50" /></div>\r\n<h3>THE CLEAR WAY</h3>\r\nTO A PERFECTLY\r\n\r\nSTRAIGHT SMILE\r\n\r\nINVISALIGN\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<h3>THE SMILE YOU''VE ALWAYS DREAMED OF WITH INVISALIGN</h3>\r\nHave you been hiding your smile because you fear othersâ€™ negative reactions? Are you not confident about the way your teeth look?\r\n\r\nIf youâ€™d like a straighter, more beautiful smile without going through traditional orthodontic treatments, Invisalign may be the answer for you.\r\n<h4>What is Invisalign?</h4>\r\nInvisalign is a revolutionary cosmetic dental treatment that uses a series of removable clear aligners (or invisible braces) to gradually straighten your teeth.\r\nIt is a far more comfortable and a lot less intrusive method than traditional orthodontic treatments. With Invisalign, you can achieve the smile of your dreams without anyone noticing youâ€™re undergoing a dental treatment.\r\n<h4>What are the benefits of Invisalign?</h4>\r\n<ul class="list-inline">\r\n	<li>Invisalign is ideal for those who have always wanted a better smile but have been putting off orthodontic treatments because of the social stigma associated with braces.</li>\r\n	<li>The durable, transparent thermoplastic material of the Invisalign aligners make them almost impossible to see and as such, a much more discreet alternative to orthodontic treatments.</li>\r\n	<li>Being completely removable, it is easy to maintain the daily oral hygiene routine needed to reduce the chance of plaque build-up, tooth decay and gum disease.</li>\r\n	<li>These invisible braces donâ€™t rely on traditional metal appliances, so food and plaque are not trapped on the surface of the teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>It is a surprisingly fast treatment, with most of our patients requiring approximately less than a year to transform their smile and be able to display their beautiful new look.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>YOUR INVISALIGN TREATMENT</h2>\r\nDuring your initial consultation at Broadway Dentalâ€™s Sydney Clinic, Dr Yassmin will gain an understanding of your current situation, and explore your goals to determine if Invisalign is suitable for you. Should this be the case, Dr Yassmin will then begin by taking detailed impressions of your teeth. These will then be digitised to create a computerised 3D image of your smile from which, Dr Yassmin will be able to determine the precise movements needed to create the best results. Subsequently, your custom-made invisible braces will be crafted according to your individual treatment plan.\r\nThe number of aligners you will need will depend on your needs and goals however, a full Invisalign treatment typically involves the use of 18 to 36 aligners, and it takes around 9 to 18 months.\r\n<h2>LIVING WITH INVISALIGN</h2>\r\nDuring your treatment, you will wear each aligner for around two weeks, day and night, with small breaks for eating, brushing and flossing your teeth, and the occasional time off for special events. After two weeks, you will then switch to the next aligner which, will move your teeth a little more.\r\nWe will ask you to come in for a check-up every 4-6 weeks so that we can monitor your progress and provide you with your next set of aligners.\r\nThroughout your treatment, you should notice small movements as the invisible braces gradually move your teeth to create an even, healthy and very attractive smile.\r\nTo find out how Invisalign can help you achieve a Hollywood smile, call us today on (02) 9281 0100 or via email.\r\n\r\n<b>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</b>\r\n<div id="accordion" class="panel-group">\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div id="headingOne" class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a href="#collapseOne" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How does Invisalign work?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">\r\n<div class="panel-body">The aligners in the Invisalign apply consistent, controlled force to individual teeth, gently moving them into their new desired position.Invisalign differs from traditional braces in that it actually controls the amount of force applied to each tooth and this reduces the length of the treatment in comparison with traditional orthodontics.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div id="headingTwo" class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" href="#collapseTwo" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How effective is Invisalign?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Studies show that out of the 1.5 million people who have had or are having Invisalign treatment, 98% of them are satisfied with the results.However, it''s important to remember that Invisalign cannot treat all orthodontic conditions such as severe over or underbites, severely tipped teeth, numerous missing teeth, or unerupted teeth.\r\n\r\nTo find out whether Invisalign is right for you, talk to the team at Broadway Dental on (02) 9281 0100 or via email.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div id="headingThree" class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" href="#collapseThree" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">What does Invisalign look like?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">The clear, strong, non-toxic plastic material Invisalign aligners are manufactured with, make them very difficult to see when worn. Besides, having been custom-made specifically for each patient according to their treatment plan, aligners fit very neatly to the teeth.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div id="headingFour" class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" href="#collapseFour" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How long does Invisalign treatment take?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Treatment times vary but on average, patients achieve straighter teeth with Invisalign in around twelve to fourteen months, four months less than traditional braces.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div id="headingFive" class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" href="#collapseFive" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">Is Invisalign painful? </a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapseFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">Wearing the Invisalign aligners is generally far more comfortable than wearing traditional braces. Minor discomfort may be experienced initially and for a few days every time a new aligner is used. This slight feeling of pressure is a sign aligners are doing their job and moving the teeth into the desired position.\r\nAny discomfort is usually relieved in a few days.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n[su_spoiler icon="arrow"]Hidden content[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n[su_spoiler icon="arrow"]Hidden content[/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="panel panel-default">\r\n<div id="headingSix" class="panel-heading">\r\n<h4 class="panel-title"><a class="collapsed" href="#collapseSix" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion">How much does Invisalign cost?</a></h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">\r\n<div class="panel-body">The cost of an Invisalign treatment depends on individual circumstances but for most of our patients at Broadway Dental, the cost of a full treatment ranges between $3000 and $10,000.After our initial consultation we''ll be able to provide you with a treatment plan detailing all costs for your specific needs.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Invisalign', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 00:07:00', '2015-09-14 00:07:00', '', 95, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
