(1023, 1, '2015-09-14 04:43:01', '2015-09-14 04:43:01', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h4>REFRESHINGÂ YOURÂ BEAUTYÂ WITHOUTÂ BARELYÂ NOTICINGÂ IT</h4>\r\n\r\nThoughÂ certainÂ injectableÂ productsÂ areÂ commonlyÂ knownÂ andÂ usedÂ forÂ smootheningÂ facialÂ wrinkles,Â someÂ ofÂ themÂ haveÂ alsoÂ foundÂ veryÂ importantÂ clinicalÂ applicationsÂ inÂ theÂ treatmentÂ ofÂ TemporomandibularÂ JointÂ SyndromeÂ andÂ BruxismÂ (teethÂ grinding).\r\n\r\n<h4>WhatÂ isÂ TemporomandibularÂ JointÂ Syndrome?</h4>\r\n\r\nTheÂ TemporomandibularÂ JointÂ (TMJ)Â isÂ theÂ jointÂ thatÂ connectsÂ theÂ jawÂ toÂ theÂ skull.Â WhenÂ weÂ talkÂ aboutÂ TemporomandibularÂ JointÂ Syndrome,Â weÂ areÂ referringÂ toÂ theÂ painÂ andÂ dysfunctionÂ ofÂ theÂ musclesÂ usedÂ inÂ theÂ masticationÂ processÂ andÂ theÂ temporomandibularÂ jointsÂ which,Â causesÂ dizzinessÂ andÂ headaches.\r\n\r\nFortunately,Â TMJÂ isÂ nowÂ treatableÂ withÂ aÂ rangeÂ ofÂ non-surgicalÂ proceduresÂ thatÂ injectÂ aÂ solutionÂ intoÂ certainÂ musclesÂ ofÂ theÂ headÂ andÂ neckÂ areasÂ toÂ leaveÂ themÂ relaxedÂ andÂ pain-free.\r\n\r\nTheÂ injectableÂ treatmentÂ forÂ TMJÂ therapyÂ doesÂ notÂ affectÂ anyÂ otherÂ partsÂ ofÂ theÂ patient''sÂ bodyÂ otherÂ thanÂ thoseÂ injected.Â However,Â dependingÂ onÂ theÂ severityÂ ofÂ theÂ headaches,Â additionalÂ injectionsÂ mayÂ beÂ appliedÂ toÂ otherÂ partsÂ ofÂ theÂ headÂ andÂ neckÂ area.Â DrÂ YassminÂ willÂ adviseÂ patientsÂ accordinglyÂ beforeÂ proceedingÂ withÂ TMJÂ treatment.\r\n\r\nTMJÂ treatmentsÂ areÂ justÂ oneÂ ofÂ theÂ manyÂ InjectableÂ treatmentsÂ availableÂ atÂ BroadwayÂ DentalÂ SydneyÂ toÂ helpÂ youÂ restoreÂ yourÂ naturalÂ beautyÂ withoutÂ barelyÂ noticingÂ it.\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>InjectableÂ treatmentsÂ canÂ alsoÂ beÂ usedÂ inÂ theÂ followingÂ cases:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>ToÂ complementÂ aestheticÂ dentistryÂ procedures,</li>\r\n	<li>AsÂ aÂ minimallyÂ invasiveÂ alternativeÂ toÂ surgicallyÂ treatingÂ highÂ lipÂ lineÂ casesÂ (gummyÂ smiles),</li>\r\n	<li>ToÂ correctÂ downturnÂ smile,</li>\r\n	<li>For