roper alignment with one another. Or you can choose to have even more veneers placed for a dramatic first impression. Placing veneers on straightened teeth also makes them easier to care for and longer-lasting. If teeth are crowded when veneers are placed over them, you risk the chance of having an improper bite that wears down your beautiful new teeth. When your teeth bite together properly, the veneers will fit together correctly as well.</p>\r\n<h2>What to Expect from Treatment</h2>\r\n<p>So how long will your treatment take to complete? Thankfully, convenient orthodontic options like <a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/treatments/invisalign/invisalign-works/">Invisalign can help you easily and quickly straighten your smile</a> without having to wear conventional braces. Most adults achieve desirable results in just 12-18 months. You can even whiten your smile at the same time! Since Invisalign is removable, meals and home care continue as normal without any interruption from brackets and wires. As the teeth straightening comes to a close, your porcelain veneers can be completed in just two appointments. Theyâ€™re the perfect way to finish off your goal toward a healthier, more beautiful smile.</p>\r\n<p>Are you considering teeth straightening and porcelain veneers? Youâ€™re not alone! Broadway Dental has helped thousands of adults achieve beautiful new smiles. We are happy to discuss options with you and provide you with a no-pressure treatment plan that meets your needs. <strong><a href="http://broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">Schedule your smile assessment</a> with Dr Yassmin today!</strong></p>\r\n', 'Smile Whitening and Veneers Compliment Your Smile', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '937-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 06:33:42', '2015-09-14 06:33:42', '', 937, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/937-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1061, 1, '2015-09-14 06:39:01', '2015-09-14 06:39:01', '<div class="treatments">\r\n								<h2>Treatment provided</h2>\r\n								<div class="treatments-provided">\r\n									<ul>\r\n<li>Photos and Radiographic records</li>\r\n<li>Photos and radiographic records were taken to allow accurate assessment of the existing dentition (development and arrangement of teeth in his mouth) and to give Donald a visual view of the treatment needed.</li>\r\n<li>Preventative care (Dental prophylaxis)</li>\r\n<li>Deep scaling and polishing to remove the buildup of heavy plaque (also known as calculus and tartar) and staining on Donald''s teeth, helping prevent cavities and gum disease</li>\r\n<li>Oral hygiene routine - Cariscreen and caries free rinse program. Custom trays of GC tooth mousse were created for home use, which will help prevent tooth decay (that can lead to cavities, pain, tooth loss and infection) and minimise intrinsic staining (white specs on teeth).</li>\r\n<li>Extractions -Removal of highly infected teeth was performed to enable a healthy mouth.</li>\r\n<li>Upper and lower partial denture - Due to the tight time frame an upper and lower partial denture was made. Valplast dentures were made for a highly aesthetic and functional result.</li>\r\n<li>Teeth whitening - BriteSmile whitening system was used to whiten Donald''s teeth. Custom trays were also made to give Donald a whitening maintenance program to take home to help sustain his whiter smile.</li>\r\n</ul>									<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/contact-us/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n								</div>\r\n								</div>', 'EPISODE 3 DONALD', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'episode-3-donald', '', '', '2015-09-28 08:15:17', '2015-09-28 08:15:17', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?post_type=video&#038;p=1061', 0, 'video', '', 0),
(1062, 1, '2015-09-14 06:36:12', '2015-09-14 06:36:12', 'When I first began my career in dentistry I had no idea where it would take me. What takes a keen eye and an artistic hand can still be improved when other contributing factors are at play. My vision for impeccable cosmetic and rehabilitative oral care lead me to pursue many post-graduate opportunities that widened my knowledge as well as my skill. Ultimately I chose to expand my capabilities even further by seeking a Masters of Aesthetic Dentistry from Kings College of London.\r\nThe reason why I chose this programme was because of its rigorous demand for achieving perfection in dental aesthetics. Only the most dedicated dentists are accepted and the study is lead by a team of leading global aesthetic dentists. In addition to already being a licensed dentist, students had to dedicate extensive research, face-to-face training, clinical requirements and a dissertation over the course of 3 years. It meant making a huge investment for myself and for the future of my vision as a dentist.\r\nAs it came down to my final year, I finalised my dissertation on whitening processes. What I learned through my dissertation helped me to appreciate even the minutest details of otherwise â€œroutineâ€ cosmetic dentistry procedures.\r\nMy dissertation was focused on teeth whitening.&amp;nbsp;During the process I discovered that&amp;nbsp;I could begin changing the way that I cared for patients due to the new techniques that I could utilise.\r\nSince completing my Masters of Aesthetic Dentistry, I have been able to implement new techniques that provide my patients with services that look more natural than ever. This involves a wide range of procedures such as porcelain veneers, dental implant prosthesis (such as All-on-4 dentures), composite bonding and whitening, just to name a few. What may not work for one dentist doesnâ€™t mean that it isnâ€™t possible. It just means that they may not have the skills to do so. My graduate training allowed me to reach a level of comprehensive restorative and aesthetic goals that most dentists wonâ€™t ever achieve.\r\nIt has been a great honour to take what I already felt extremely confident in as a dentist and make it even better. My capabilities and confidence for cosmetic and rehabilitative oral care allow me to offer therapies unlike any other in the area. Experience and wisdom shared with me by my mentors have made Broadway Dental into something so great that even I would not have envisioned it. It is truly a great honour to have the potential to change the lives of so many people. Not only am I capable of enriching the health of their teeth, I am giving them back the confidence that they need from a beautiful smile. Saying that my career is rewarding is an understatement!\r\nI greatly appreciate the sense of appreciation and friendship that I have been able to develop with all of my current patients. As we move forward into the future of Broadway Dental, I know we will continue to see many exciting new things to come!\r\n', 'The Other Side of Dentistry by Dr. Fadi Yassmin', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '935-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 06:36:12', '2015-09-14 06:36:12', '', 935, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/935-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1063, 1, '2015-09-14 06:41:07', '2015-09-14 06:41:07', '<div class="treatments">\r\n								<h2>Treatment provided</h2>\r\n								<div class="treatments-provided">\r\n									<ul>\r\n<li>Photos and Radiographic records</li>\r\n<li>Photos and radiographic records were taken to allow accurate assessment of the existing dentition (development and arrangement of teeth in his mouth) and to give John a visual view of the treatment needed.</li>\r\n<li>Preventative care (Dental prophylaxis)</li>\r\n<li>Deep scaling and polishing to remove the buildup of heavy plaque (also known as calculus and tartar) and staining on John''s teeth, helping prevent cavities, further tooth loss and gum disease</li>\r\n<li>Oral hygiene routine - Cariscreen and caries free rinse program. Custom trays of GC tooth mousse were created for home use, which will help prevent tooth decay (that can lead to cavities, pain, tooth loss and infection) and minimise intrinsic staining (white specs on teeth).</li>\r\n<li>Bridge -John was given a new 4 unit bridge to close the visible gap on the right side of his mouth. The material used has a zirconia framework which greatly increases strength whilst also providing optimum aesthetics. The dental bridge was used to replace John''s missing teeth and was fixed into his mouth via adjoining crowns. A custom shade is taken of the teeth to allow the crowns and bridges to be matched creating a natural looking smile.</li>\r\n<li>Teeth whitening - BriteSmile whitening of John''s teeth to perfectly match the custom crown and bridge work performed. Custom trays were also made to give John a take home whitening maintenance program to help sustain his whiter smile.</li>\r\n</ul>									<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/contact-us/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n								</div>\r\n								</div>', 'EPISODE 4 JOHN', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'episode-4-john', '', '', '2015-09-28 08:15:30', '2015-09-28 08:15:30', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?post_type=video&#038;p=1063', 0, 'video', '', 0),
(1064, 1, '2015-09-14 06:40:25', '2015-09-14 06:40:25', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>IMPROVING THE HEALTH AND BEAUTY OF YOUR SMILE</h3>\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental we are convinced that when you look great, you feel terrific.\r\n\r\nAnd of course, your smile is one of the features that can make the biggest impact on your appearance and on the way you interact with others - personally and professionally.\r\n\r\nBroadway Dental provides an extensive choice of cosmetic treatments, all of which can improve your oral health, and help create a beautiful Hollywood smile that you''ll be proud to show off wherever you go.\r\n\r\nWhether you''d simply like a brighter smile, or you could benefit from a complete smile makeover, the Broadway Dental Sydney team have the know-how and the technology to give you the smile design you''ve always dreamed of.\r\n\r\n<h3>What type of treatments do we use to achieve celebrity smiles?</h3>\r\n\r\n<h4>DENTAL IMPLANTS</h4>\r\n\r\nAn excellent option for restoring one or more missing teeth, dental implants act as a solid new root for a new tooth restoration. Essentially tiny titanium screws, dental implants are surgically placed into your jawbone and secured once they have bonded. This creates a seamless look and feel and can greatly improve your smile and your overall looks.\r\n\r\nFollowing the dental implant procedure, Dr Yassmin can then restore your tooth using a porcelain crown or bridge. After the crown or bridge is in place, you can once again enjoy a complete, healthy and natural-looking smile.\r\n\r\n<h4>INVISALIGN</h4>\r\n\r\nIf you''d like a straighter, more even smile but you''ve been put off by the clumsy look of traditional braces, Invisalign is the answer.\r\n\r\nInvisalign uses clear, medical-grade plastic aligners that are practically invisible, to gradually and efficiently straighten your teeth without any heavy metal brackets. It''s also completely removable, so that you can take your aligners out to eat, brush and floss as normal.\r\n\r\nNow you can join the hundreds of adult patients we''ve helped achieve a more beautiful, straighter smile - invisibly.\r\nIf you would like to find out how Invisalign could give you the smile you''ve always wanted, just give us a call and speak to the Broadway Dental team to arrange your personal consultation today.\r\n\r\n<h4>DENTAL BONDING</h4>\r\n\r\nOne of our most cost-effective cosmetic dental procedures, dental bonding uses tooth-coloured resin to repair or improve the appearance of your teeth.Dental bonding may be a smart option:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Restore decayed, chipped or cracked teeth</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	<li>Lighten discoloured teeth</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Change the shape of teeth</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Protect your tooth''s root if your gums have receded</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Provide alternatives to traditional porcelain veneers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\nDr Yassmin will select the coloured composite resin that most closely matches your natural tooth. The resin will then be applied and hardened with a special light to securely bond the material to your tooth. Once the material has hardened, Dr Yassmin will shape and trim the resin, and finally polish it to a sheen which, closely matches the rest of your natural tooth.\r\n\r\nBroadway Dental Sydney offers dental bonding to improve the look of your smile without the need for expensive and expensive custom-made tooth restorations. The procedure is completely straightforward, and most patients require no anaesthesia to remain comfortable throughout the procedure.\r\n\r\n<h4>TEETH WHITENING</h4>\r\n\r\nMany simple everyday actions like drinking tea, coffee and red wine, or smoking, can stain your teeth and leave you with a dull smile you''ll be hesitant to show off.\r\n\r\nThe Broadway Dental Teeth Whitening treatment will lighten your teeth by up to 12 shades, improving your self-confidence and giving you a dazzling new smile you''ll be proud to share with the world.\r\n\r\nWe offer two very safe and effective methods of teeth whitening:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>  In-chair whitening - you will be able to enjoy a new smile in just over an hour</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>At-home treatments - improve the colour of your smile in as little as two weeks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>DENTAL VENEERS</h4>\r\n\r\nStained, discoloured and crooked teeth can wreck your confidence and lower your self-esteem, but you do not have to live with the shame one day longer. At Broadway Dental, we can provide the dental veneers you need to restore your bright white smile, your appearance and your self-confidence.\r\n\r\nOur dental veneers, including traditional, porcelain and composite options, can also restore your great smile if your teeth are chipped, broken or worn. Even if your teeth are gappy or misaligned, our porcelain dental veneers can restore your great smile and give you the confidence you need to face the world.\r\n\r\nOur custom-made dental veneers are durable yet incredibly thin. Once these thin porcelain shells are bonded to your teeth securely, it will give them a natural look and feel. You will not even know you are wearing them - and neither will anyone else.\r\n\r\nIt will not take much time to transform your smile from embarrassing to bright and white. Even if your teeth or chipped, cracked or damaged, our custom-made dental veneers can transform your smile in just two appointments.\r\n\r\n<h4>SLEEP DENTISTRY</h4>\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental, we offer a full range of sleep and sedation dentistry, including traditional sleep dentistry, the latest in sedation dentistry and GA. These practices are perfect for the fearful dental patient, but they can be a wonderful choice even for men and women who are comfortable with regular dental care.\r\n\r\nAt Broadway Dental, we understand that a simple trip to the dentist is not so simple for many patients. Whether it is a bad experience in the past or just a generalized fear of the dentist chair, we understand the trepidation many patients experience when scheduling dental care.\r\n\r\nThat is why we work so hard to ease the fears of our patients - and why we offer a full range of options designed to eliminate pain and reduce the fear associated with dental care. From sleep dentistry to sedation and GA, Broadway Dental offers a full range of services designed to help you sit back, relax and regain your healthy smile.\r\n\r\nPatients who have tried sleep dentistry typically wonder what all the fuss was about. Far from being fearful, these patients actually look forward to their dental appointments. They know they will experience no pain - and they know that in the end they will emerge with a bright white smile they will be proud to show their friends, family members and co-workers.\r\n\r\nSome patients worry about the loss of control they will feel when undergoing cosmetic or therapeutic procedures using sleep dentistry, but they need not fret. When undergoing sleep dentistry treatment, the patient has the sensation of being asleep, but they remain awake and able to respond to the dentist at all times. This makes the dental procedures more effective and safer for everyone involved.\r\n\r\n<b>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</b>\r\n[su_accordion]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="What is cosmetic dentistry?" style="fancy"] Simply put, cosmetic dentistry refers to the art and science used at Broadway Dental to create a more beautiful smile for you.\r\n\r\nCosmetic dentistry can lighten stained teeth, correct crooked or replace missing teeth, or create a complete smile makeover.\r\n\r\nSmile design from Broadway Dental Sydney starts with a personalised cosmetic dentistry treatment plan, based on the needs and goals you have for your smile. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="How can cosmetic dentistry improve my smile??" style="fancy"]If youâ€™re living with teeth which are damaged, worn or need rebuilding, we may recommend Dental Crowns, Inlays or Onlays.\r\n\r\nTo improve the colour or shape of your teeth, dental veneers, Teeth Whitening or bonding could be the right option for you.\r\n\r\nIf you are missing teeth, we can use Dental Implants, Bridges or Dentures to restore your smile.\r\n\r\nWe will evaluate your personal situation and help you decide on the right combination of treatments for your smile. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="Why are my teeth becoming darker as I get older?" style="fancy"] \r\n      \r\n      Many factors act upon your teeth to make them look dull and less bright over time:\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Plaque tends to build up faster and more heavily as we age</li>\r\n<li> Red wine, tea and coffee will stain your teeth the more you drink them</li>\r\n<li>The dentin that makes up your teeth will also change and darken naturally over time</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAll of these factors can be addressed with the help of professional teeth whitening from Broadway Dental.\r\n      \r\n      \r\n       [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="How long will my teeth whitening treatment last?" style="fancy"]As with any dental procedure, your results will depend on your individual situation, and your oral care routine post-treatment. Continuing with the habits that stained your teeth in the first place, such as drinking coffee or red wine, or especially smoking, will gradually stain your teeth again over time. Avoiding these habits, and visiting Broadway Dental for periodic touch-up treatment, can help preserve your white new smile. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="Is cosmetic dentistry right for me?" style="fancy"]Thanks to the extensive range of advanced dental procedures and technology available today, almost anyone can benefit from cosmetic dentistry in our Sydney practice.\r\n\r\nSo whether youâ€™d like a brighter smile, or whether you need to replace missing teeth, your first step is to arrange a consultation with Dr Yassmin and the Broadway Dental team. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[/su_accordion]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Cosmetic Dentistry', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 06:40:25', '2015-09-14 06:40:25', '', 125, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/125-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1065, 1, '2015-09-14 06:42:24', '2015-09-14 06:42:24', '<div class="treatments">\r\n								<h2>Treatment provided</h2>\r\n								<div class="treatments-provided">\r\n									<ul>\r\n<li>Photos and Radiographic records</li>\r\n<li>Photos and radiographic records were taken to allow accurate assessment of the existing dentition (development and arrangement of teeth in his mouth) and to give Chris a visual view of the treatment needed.</li>\r\n<li>Preventative care (Dental prophylaxis)</li>\r\n<li>Deep scaling and polishing to remove the buildup of heavy plaque (also known as calculus and tartar) and staining on Chris'' teeth, helping prevent cavities and gum disease</li>\r\n<li>Oral hygiene routine - Cariscreen and caries free rinse program. Custom trays of GC tooth mousse were created for home use, which will help prevent tooth decay (that can lead to cavities, pain, tooth loss and infection) and minimise intrinsic staining (white specs on teeth).</li>\r\n<li>Crown - Four Dental crowns were placed in cases where large fillings were not an option. This was an excellent way to restore and retain Chris'' teeth whilst also achieving a highly aesthetic appearance.</li>\r\n<li>Aesthetic Recontouring - Reshaping the teeth by adding white filling material and gently disking teeth.</li>\r\n<li>Teeth whitening - BriteSmile whitening system was used to whiten Chris'' teeth. Custom trays were also made to give Chris a whitening maintenance program to take home to help sustain his whiter smile.</li>\r\n</ul>									<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/contact-us/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n								</div>\r\n								</div>', 'EPISODE 5 CHRIS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'episode-5-chris', '', '', '2015-09-28 08:15:42', '2015-09-28 08:15:42', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?post_type=video&#038;p=1065', 0, 'video', '', 0),
(1066, 1, '2015-09-14 06:42:48', '2015-09-14 06:42:48', '<div class="row inn_vide inn_contant">\r\n<div class="col-md-8 "><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8XH0-kzg8jw?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;controls=1&amp;autohide=1" width="100%" height="280" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>\r\n<div class="col-lg-4 inn_page_invs">\r\n<div class="image-logo"><img src="http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/invs_img.jpg" alt="invs_img" width="200" height="50" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-99" /></div>\r\n<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>THE CLEAR WAY</h3>\r\nTO A PERFECTLY\r\nSTRAIGHT SMILE\r\nINVISALIGN</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-lg-12">\r\n<h3>THE SMILE YOU''VE ALWAYS DREAMED OF WITH INVISALIGN</h3>\r\nHave you been hiding your smile because you fear othersâ€™ negative reactions? Are you not confident about the way your teeth look?\r\n\r\nIf youâ€™d like a straighter, more beautiful smile without going through traditional orthodontic treatments, Invisalign may be the answer for you.\r\n<h4>What is Invisalign?</h4>\r\nInvisalign is a revolutionary cosmetic dental treatment that uses a series of removable clear aligners (or invisible braces) to gradually straighten your teeth.\r\nIt is a far more comfortable and a lot less intrusive method than traditional orthodontic treatments. With Invisalign, you can achieve the smile of your dreams without anyone noticing youâ€™re undergoing a dental treatment.\r\n<h4>What are the benefits of Invisalign?</h4>\r\n<ul class="list-inline">\r\n	<li>Invisalign is ideal for those who have always wanted a better smile but have been putting off orthodontic treatments because of the social stigma associated with braces.</li>\r\n	<li>The durable, transparent thermoplastic material of the Invisalign aligners make them almost impossible to see and as such, a much more discreet alternative to orthodontic treatments.</li>\r\n	<li>Being completely removable, it is easy to maintain the daily oral hygiene routine needed to reduce the chance of plaque build-up, tooth decay and gum disease.</li>\r\n	<li>These invisible braces donâ€™t rely on traditional metal appliances, so food and plaque are not trapped on the surface of the teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>It is a surprisingly fast treatment, with most of our patients requiring approximately less than a year to transform their smile and be able to display their beautiful new look.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>YOUR INVISALIGN TREATMENT</h4>\r\nDuring your initial consultation at Broadway Dentalâ€™s Sydney Clinic, Dr Yassmin will gain an understanding of your current situation, and explore your goals to determine if Invisalign is suitable for you. Should this be the case, Dr Yassmin will then begin by taking detailed impressions of your teeth. These will then be digitised to create a computerised 3D image of your smile from which, Dr Yassmin will be able to determine the precise movements needed to create the best results. Subsequently, your custom-made invisible braces will be crafted according to your individual treatment plan.\r\nThe number of aligners you will need will depend on your needs and goals however, a full Invisalign treatment typically involves the use of 18 to 36 aligners, and it takes around 9 to 18 months.\r\n<h4>LIVING WITH INVISALIGN</h4>\r\nDuring your treatment, you will wear each aligner for around two weeks, day and night, with small breaks for eating, brushing and flossing your teeth, and the occasional time off for special events. After two weeks, you will then switch to the next aligner which, will move your teeth a little more.\r\nWe will ask you to come in for a check-up every 4-6 weeks so that we can monitor your progress and provide you with your next set of aligners.\r\nThroughout your treatment, you should notice small movements as the invisible braces gradually move your teeth to create an even, healthy and very attractive smile.\r\nTo find out how Invisalign can help you achieve a Hollywood smile, call us today on (02) 9281 0100 or via email.\r\n\r\n<h4>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</h4>\r\n\r\n[su_accordion]\r\n  [su_spoiler title="How does Invisalign work?" style="fancy"]  The aligners in the Invisalign apply consistent, controlled force to individual teeth, gently moving them into their new desired position.\r\n\r\nInvisalign differs from traditional braces in that it actually controls the amount of force applied to each tooth and this reduces the length of the treatment in comparison with traditional orthodontics. [/su_spoiler]\r\n\r\n  [su_spoiler title="Spoiler title" style="fancy"] Studies show that out of the 1.5 million people who have had or are having Invisalign treatment, 98% of them are satisfied with the results.However, itâ€™s important to remember that Invisalign cannot treat all orthodontic conditions such as severe over or underbites, severely tipped teeth, numerous missing teeth, or unerupted teeth.\r\n\r\nTo find out whether Invisalign is right for you, talk to the team at Broadway Dental on (02) 9281 0100 or via email. [/su_spoiler]\r\n  [su_spoiler title="What does Invisalign look like?" style="fancy"]The clear, strong, non-toxic plastic material Invisalign aligners are manufactured with, make them very difficult to see when worn. Besides, having been custom-made specifically for each patient according to their treatment plan, aligners fit very neatly to the teeth. [/su_spoiler]\r\n   [su_spoiler title="How long does Invisalign treatment take?" style="fancy"] Treatment times vary but on average, patients achieve straighter teeth with Invisalign in around twelve to fourteen months, four months less than traditional braces.[/su_spoiler]\r\n    [su_spoiler title="Is Invisalign painful? " style="fancy"]Wearing the Invisalign aligners is generally far more comfortable than wearing traditional braces. Minor discomfort may be experienced initially and for a few days every time a new aligner is used. This slight feeling of pressure is a sign aligners are doing their job and moving the teeth into the desired position.\r\nAny discomfort is usually relieved in a few days. [/su_spoiler]\r\n      [su_spoiler title="How much does Invisalign cost?" style="fancy"] The cost of an Invisalign treatment depends on individual circumstances but for most of our patients at Broadway Dental, the cost of a full treatment ranges between $3000 and $10,000.After our initial consultation weâ€™ll be able to provide you with a treatment plan detailing all costs for your specific needs. [/su_spoiler]\r\n[/su_accordion]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', 'Invisalign', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '95-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 06:42:48', '2015-09-14 06:42:48', '', 95, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/95-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
