(1081, 1, '2015-09-14 07:20:16', '2015-09-14 07:20:16', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>Throw away your old dentures</h3>\r\n\r\nFor many people dentures are cumbersome, uncomfortable and constantly loose, making them feel uneasy about smiling and eating, while missing teeth can compromise on your oral and general health.\r\n<h4>WHY ALL ON 4?</h4>\r\nThere are many benefits to choosing the All-On-4 System. Some include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>They look, feel and function just like natural teeth</li>\r\n	<li>Aid in helping to keep your jaw bone strong</li>\r\n	<li>Virtually eliminates the need for bone grafting, which is invasive, and adds to recovery time</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to clean and maintain good oral health</li>\r\n	<li>Less expensive than traditional dental implants as fewer implants are required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThe All-On-4 System from Broadway Dental can give you a complete smile once again and help you regain your confidence. Unlike a denture which is held by adhesive and a bridge, which relies on healthy teeth for support, the All-On-4 System of prosthetics is permanently secured with dental implants.\r\n</div>', 'Benifits of All on 4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '133-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 07:20:16', '2015-09-14 07:20:16', '', 133, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/133-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1082, 1, '2015-09-14 07:21:08', '2015-09-14 07:21:08', '<div class="treatments-provided">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Photos and Radiographic records</li>\r\n	<li>Photos and radiographic records were taken to allow accurate assessment of the existing dentition (development and arrangement of teeth in her mouth) and to give Tracey a visual view of the treatment needed.</li>\r\n	<li>Preventative care (Dental prophylaxis)</li>\r\n	<li>Deep scaling and polishing to remove the buildup of heavy plaque (also known as calculus and tartar) and staining on Tracey''s teeth, helping prevent cavities and gum disease</li>\r\n	<li>Oral hygiene routine - Cariscreen and caries free rinse program. Custom trays of GC tooth mousse were created for home use, which will help prevent tooth decay (that can lead to cavities, pain, tooth loss and infection) and minimise intrinsic staining (white specs on teeth).</li>\r\n	<li>White fillings - To rejuvenate her teeth, broken amalgam fillings were replaced with white fillings for a more natural, comfortable smile. Made from premise(composite) these new fillings are also free from any trace of mercury.</li>\r\n	<li>Aesthetic Recontouring - Reshaping the teeth by adding white filling material and gently discing teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>Teeth whitening - BriteSmile whitening system was used to whiten Tracey''s teeth. Custom trays were also made to give Tracey a whitening maintenance program to take home to help sustain her whiter smile.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a class="book-now" title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" href="http://www.broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">book your consultation today</a>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>\r\n</div>', '10 Years Younger in 10 days', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '155-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 07:21:08', '2015-09-14 07:21:08', '', 155, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/155-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1083, 1, '2015-09-14 07:25:27', '2015-09-14 07:25:27', '<div class="inn_contant">							\n\n<h3>ALL ON 4 TREATMENT PROCESS<h3>\n\nPlacing your dental implants is a minimally invasive procedure that can be completed in a single appointment here at the Broadway Dental purpose-built All-on-4 clinic.\nEvery surgery is unique and will be tailored to your specific needs and circumstance.\nÂ \nReceiving your implants can take between three and six hours. The expected timeframe to place all of your implants is reliant on many factors and will be discussed with you in detail during your assessment appointments.\nÂ \nAt Broadway Dental, we perform our All-On-4 procedures under general anaesthetic, providing a greater level of safety and comfort to our patients. General anaesthesia has a number of important benefits for this type of procedure when compared with sedation, sometimes referred to as Sleep Dentistry.\nÂ \nAfter making a incision in the gum, and using a special customised guide, each implant is placed into its precise location in the jawbone. Our in-house laboratory allows us to prepare your permanent teeth within 24 hours, so you can start enjoying your brighter and whiter smile right away.\n									\n										<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://www.broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">book your consultation today</a>\n\n									\n									\n									\n									\n							', 'The Treatment Process', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '194-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-14 07:25:27', '2015-09-14 07:25:27', '', 194, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/194-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
