(1123, 1, '2015-09-15 01:02:03', '2015-09-15 01:02:03', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h4>ALL ON FOUR DENTAL IMPLANTS EXPLAINED:</h4>\r\nLiving with the stigma that comes with missing teeth? Too embarrassed to be seen in public without your full smile?\r\nFor many years dentures have been the preferred solution for the replacement of missing teeth:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Complete dentures are used by people who have lost all their natural upper or lower teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>Partial dentures are for patients who still retain some of their natural teeth.</li>\r\n	<li>Severely damaged teeth</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced periodontal disease</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nAlthough dentures are still popular, Dental Implants are quickly becoming one of the most sought after tooth replacement options today. Replicating a missing tooth root, Dental Implants are fine titanium screws or rods that are placed into the jawbone.\r\nThe latest innovation in modern dentistry- All-on-4\r\nBringing dentures and dental implants together, All-On-4 Implant Retained Dentures, enable patients to have a set of upper or lower dentures permanently secured, sometimes with as few as four Dental Implants.\r\n<h4>How is this achieved?</h4>\r\nSimply by placing two of the four implants at an angle at the front of the mouth where the jawbone is denser and stronger.\r\n<h4>How do I maintain my All-on-4 Implant Retained Dentures?</h4>\r\nAfter receiving your All-on-4 Implant Retained Dentures, it is essential you follow a thorough at-home brushing and flossing routine. You should also schedule regular appointment check-ups every six months with Dr Yassmin to ensure your implants remain strong.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about All-on-4 and find out if you''re an ideal candidate to use them, schedule a consultation appointment with Dr Yassmin who will explain the procedure in non-medical terms and gladly answer any of your questions.\r\n\r\nPlease note: Any surgical or invasive procedure carries risks. Before proceeding, you should seek a second opinion from an appropriately qualified health practitioner.\r\n</div>', 'All-On-4â„¢', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '14-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-15 01:02:03', '2015-09-15 01:02:03', '', 14, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/14-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
