(1125, 1, '2015-09-15 01:03:23', '2015-09-15 01:03:23', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\n<h3>REFRESHING YOUR BEAUTY WITHOUT BARELY NOTICING IT</h3>\r\n\r\nThough certain injectable products are commonly known and used for smoothening facial wrinkles, some of them have also found very important clinical applications in the treatment of Temporomandibular Joint Syndrome and Bruxism (teeth grinding).\r\n\r\n<h4>What is Temporomandibular Joint Syndrome?</h4>\r\n\r\nThe Temporomandibular Joint (TMJ) is the joint that connects the jaw to the skull. When we talk about Temporomandibular Joint Syndrome, we are referring to the pain and dysfunction of the muscles used in the mastication process and the temporomandibular joints which, causes dizziness and headaches.\r\n\r\nFortunately, TMJ is now treatable with a range of non-surgical procedures that inject a solution into certain muscles of the head and neck areas to leave them relaxed and pain-free.\r\n\r\nThe injectable treatment for TMJ therapy does not affect any other parts of the patient''s body other than those injected. However, depending on the severity of the headaches, additional injections may be applied to other parts of the head and neck area. Dr Yassmin will advise patients accordingly before proceeding with TMJ treatment.\r\n\r\nTMJ treatments are just one of the many Injectable treatments available at Broadway Dental Sydney to help you restore your natural beauty without barely noticing it.\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4>Injectable treatments can also be used in the following cases:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To complement aesthetic dentistry procedures,</li>\r\n	<li>As a minimally invasive alternative to surgically treating high lip line cases (gummy smiles),</li>\r\n	<li>To correct downturn smile,</li>\r\n	<li>For Lip augmentation procedures, and</li>\r\n	<li>In some orthodontic cases where facial muscles need to be retrained.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Injectable Treatments', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '237-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-15 01:03:23', '2015-09-15 01:03:23', '', 237, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/237-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1126, 1, '2015-09-15 01:09:16', '2015-09-15 01:09:16', '<div class="inn_contant">\n<h3>A STRAIGHT AND HEALTHY SMILE TO LAST A LIFETIME</h3>\n<p>Have you ever stopped to think about the kind of effect your smile has on your personal and professional life?<br>\nIndeed, your smile has a dramatic effect on the way others react towards you and, ultimately, on your self-esteem.</p>\n<p>So, if you feel itâ€™s time to make a better impression with a dashing smile, itâ€™s time to talk to Dr Yassmin about Orthodontic Treatments.</p>\n<h4>What are Orthodontic Treatments?</h4>\n<p>While initially designed to treat misaligned teeth in pre-teens and teens, today Orthodontics covers the detection and treatment of teeth and jaw misalignments and irregularities in grown-ups as well.</p>\n<p>Thatâ€™s why today many adults are choosing to undergo orthodontics &ndash; to help them achieve that beautiful straight smile they have always wanted but never had an opportunity to correct in their younger years.</p>\n<h4>What about Orofacial orthopaedics?</h4>\n<p>Using specialised custom appliances during the growth spurt of a child, a narrow or tapered arch of a child can be widen and the jaw brought forward. If the problem is treated early enough, orofacial orthopaedics can minimise or eliminate the need for secured braces in the future.</p>\n<p>These type of appliances can also be used in adults to align the teeth in a more favourable position as a prelude to braces which, are later used to correct rotation, crowding and gaps amongst teeth.</p>\n<p>Whether for your child or for you, there are many options available to help you correct dental imperfections. Find out which one of them best suits your needs by discussing your circumstances with Dr Yassmin.</p>\n\n\n<h4>benefits of<br>orthodontics</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Improve patientsâ€™ smile/self-confidence,</li>\n<li>Improve the width of the dental arches, </li>\n<li>Influence growth of the jaws to the ideal position, </li>\n<li>Reduce or eliminate the need to extract permanent teeth, </li>\n<li>Lower the risk of injury to protruded front teeth, </li>\n<li>Reduce the likelihood of impacted permanent teeth, </li>\n<li>Correct oral habits,</li>\n<li>Reduce appearance-consciousness during critical developmental years.</li>\n</ul>								\n\n<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="#">book your free consultation</a>\n<a title="Orthodontics Sydney Cases" class="book-now" href="#">See Our Orthodontics Success Stories </a>\n																	</div>', 'Orthodontics', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '813-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-15 01:09:16', '2015-09-15 01:09:16', '', 813, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/813-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
