(1271, 1, '2015-09-28 07:44:39', '2015-09-28 07:44:39', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\nEnjoying every day treats such as drinking coffee, tea or red wine, eating chocolate and other certain coloured foods can leave your teeth less bright than they once were or youâ€™d like them to be. Smoking is also a major contributing factor to the staining of your teeth.\r\nTeeth Whitening is a popular treatment option that many people choose to undertake. It is a safe and simple process that can lighten your teeth by up to 10 shades. The improvement can be seen immediately and, with your new whiter teeth, you may not be able to stop smiling.\r\nAt Broadway Dental Dr Yassmin is able to safely counteract this process and whiten your teeth by offering you two simple and effective options.\r\n<h3>TAKE HOME TEETH WHITENING: CUSTOMISED TRAYS</h3>\r\n\r\nThis simple and affordable process delivers stunning results. Take home teeth whitening is achieved by using a gel similar to the BrightSmile gel, which is applied to your teeth using customised trays â€“ which look like thin mouthguards.\r\n\r\nThese trays fit precisely to the shape of your teeth and can be worn in the comfort of your own home at times to suit your busy schedule. The gel will gently whiten your teeth over a period of approximately 10 â€“ 12 days.\r\n\r\nAlthough the results can last for some time it is not permanent. The take home teeth whitening option can be also used to freshen-up and maintain your BrightSmile teeth whitening results.\r\n\r\nBrightSmile and take home teeth whitening is only effective on natural tooth enamel, and many people who choose to whiten their smile also replace fillings, crowns and other restorations. These are done after the BrightSmile and take home teeth whitening process in completed so your new restorations match the colour of your brighter smile exactly.\r\n\r\nDr Yassmin can offer advice on replacing your restorations for an even coloured smile.\r\n\r\nIf you think that BrightSmile or take home teeth whitening is for you then contact our team to schedule an appointment today.\r\n</div>', 'Do you want whiter teeth?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'do-you-want-whiter-teeth', '', '', '2015-09-28 07:46:45', '2015-09-28 07:46:45', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?p=1271', 0, 'post', '', 0),
