(1275, 1, '2015-09-28 07:54:41', '2015-09-28 07:54:41', '<div class="inn_contant">\r\nCosmetic Dentistry is a fusion of art and science giving you the smile youâ€™ve always wanted.\r\n\r\nYou, as the patient present to us as a dental puzzle and our aim is to provide a solution via our multidisciplinary cosmetic dentistry approach to achieve not only an aesthetic result, but just as importantly a functional healthy smile. The solution may be simple or complex.\r\n\r\nThe term Cosmetic Dentistry covers a wide range of treatment solutions, all designed to enhance the appearance as well as the health of your smile. For Cosmetic Dentist Dr Fadi Yassmin and the Broadway Dental team in Sydney, Cosmetic Dentistry is a blend of science, modern dental techniques, creativity and vision.\r\n\r\nCosmetic dentistry is not just about making your teeth white or appear straight. Dr Yassmin may employ many different cosmetic dental techniques to ensure your smile not only looks beautiful but also functions correctly.\r\n\r\nCosmetic dentistry can be used to change the size, shape, and alignment of certain teeth, fill spaces between teeth, improve or correct bites, restore decayed, broken, cracked, or chipped teeth. But your smile is more than just your teeth, it is also complemented by your gums, lips and face, which frame your smile.\r\n\r\nThrough cosmetic dentistry treatments can we change the appearance of gummy smiles, while injectable treatments can reduce fine line and wrinkles for a more youthful looking smile.\r\n\r\nThrough dental implants, Dr Yassmin, Cosmetic Dentist Sydney can replace missing teeth, and using white fillings replace old, unattractive dental treatments with natural looking ones.\r\n\r\nTogether with our clinical expertise and an awareness of your own needs, we will work to give youâ€¦â€a smile to rememberâ€  â€“  Sydney Cosmetic Dentist Dr Fadi Yassmin\r\n</div>', 'Cosmetic Dentistry at our Sydney Clinic', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cosmetic-dentistry-at-our-sydney-clinic', '', '', '2015-09-28 07:58:37', '2015-09-28 07:58:37', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?p=1275', 0, 'post', '', 0),
