(1281, 1, '2015-09-28 08:07:19', '2015-09-28 08:07:19', 'Invisalign Sydney â€“ Achieving a beautiful straight smile without compromising on appearance has led to Invisalign becoming the orthodontic treatment of choice for adults and teens.\r\n\r\nInvisalign consists of a series of clear, virtually indictable custom-moulded aligners made using advanced 3-D computer imaging software. This enables Dr Yassmin at Broadway Dental Sydney to outline your entire procedure progression on screen before your treatment even commences.\r\n\r\nThe primary concern people have about dental braces is the aesthetic impact of the metalwork on their smile. Adults especially who desire a straight smile are reluctant to undergo orthodontic treatment due to the appearance metal braces would have on social and professional situations.\r\n\r\nInvisalign consists of a series of clear, virtually indictable custom-moulded aligners made using advanced 3-D computer imaging software. This enables Dr Yassmin to outline your entire procedure progression on screen before your treatment even commences.\r\n\r\nWith Invisalign this is no longer a concern. Each set of aligners is replaced every couple of weeks with a new set moving your teeth a little more until they have straightened to the final correct position.\r\n\r\nUnlike fixed braces Invisalign aligners are removable so you are able to eat all your favourite foods as well as brush and floss normally. Additionally, being clear means that people wonâ€™t even notice you are wearing Invisalign aligners.\r\n\r\nUsing Invisalign, you can enjoy life as well as achieve a straight smile without compromising on your appearance.\r\n\r\n', 'Invisalign Treatment', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'invisalign-treatment', '', '', '2015-09-28 08:07:19', '2015-09-28 08:07:19', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/?p=1281', 0, 'post', '', 0),
