(1287, 1, '2015-09-28 08:15:23', '2015-09-28 08:15:23', '<div class="treatments">\n								<h2>Treatment provided</h2>\n								<div class="treatments-provided">\n									<ul>\n<li>Photos and Radiographic records</li>\n<li>Photos and radiographic records were taken to allow accurate assessment of the existing dentition (development and arrangement of teeth in his mouth) and to give John a visual view of the treatment needed.</li>\n<li>Preventative care (Dental prophylaxis)</li>\n<li>Deep scaling and polishing to remove the buildup of heavy plaque (also known as calculus and tartar) and staining on John''s teeth, helping prevent cavities, further tooth loss and gum disease</li>\n<li>Oral hygiene routine - Cariscreen and caries free rinse program. Custom trays of GC tooth mousse were created for home use, which will help prevent tooth decay (that can lead to cavities, pain, tooth loss and infection) and minimise intrinsic staining (white specs on teeth).</li>\n<li>Bridge -John was given a new 4 unit bridge to close the visible gap on the right side of his mouth. The material used has a zirconia framework which greatly increases strength whilst also providing optimum aesthetics. The dental bridge was used to replace John''s missing teeth and was fixed into his mouth via adjoining crowns. A custom shade is taken of the teeth to allow the crowns and bridges to be matched creating a natural looking smile.</li>\n<li>Teeth whitening - BriteSmile whitening of John''s teeth to perfectly match the custom crown and bridge work performed. Custom trays were also made to give John a take home whitening maintenance program to help sustain his whiter smile.</li>\n</ul>									<a title="Make an Appointment with Dentist Sydney" class="book-now" href="http://www.broadwaydental.com.au/make-an-appointment/">book your consultation today</a>\n<div class="clear"></div>\n								</div>\n								</div>', 'EPISODE 4 JOHN', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1063-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-28 08:15:23', '2015-09-28 08:15:23', '', 1063, 'http://111.93.163.213/Broadwaydental/php/1063-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
